Amalungu eWelsh Assembly (AM) akhathazekile ngokubonakala njengeemaphe
Amanye amalungu eNdlu ayabhidaniswa sisigqibo sokuba isihloko sakhe kufuneka sitshintshwe sibe yiMalungu ePalamente yaseWales (MWP).
Le ngxaki ivela kwizicwangciso zokutshintsha igama leNdibano libe yiPalamente yaseWales.
Amalungu eNdlu kulo lonke icandelo lezopolitiko ayesoyika ukuba oku kunokuhlekiswa.
Elinye ilungu leNdibano yeqela lezaBasebenzi lathi iqela labo likhathazekile ukuba lihlelwe yiTwp nePwp.
Kubafundi abavela ngaphandle kweWales: IsiWales sithi twp sithetha isiyatha kanti pwp sithetha ukungcola.
Elinye ilungu leNdibano yeParty of Wales lathi iqela lakhe lonke 'lalikhathazekile' yaye licebise ngezinye iindlela.
Elinye ilungu leConservative Party yaseWales lathi iqela labo livulelekile ukutshintsha igama, kodwa lathi ukutsiba kwegama ukusuka kwi-MWP ukuya kwi-muppet kuncinci.
Kule meko, igama elithi w ngesiWales lifana nelithi u ngesiNgesi saseYorkshire.
IKomishoni yeNdibano, esenza imithetho yokutshintsha amagama, ithi: Kwakhona, isigqibo sokugqibela malunga naliphi na inqaku elichaza amagama amalungu eNdibano siya kuba semthethweni kumalungu ngokwawo.
Umthetho ka-2017 woRhulumente waseWales wanika iNdibano yaseWales igunya lokutshintsha igama layo.
NgoJuni, iKomishoni yapapasha iziphumo zophando olwenziwa esidlangalaleni lweziphakamiso ezibonisa inkxaso ebanzi yokubiza iPalamente yaseWales kwiNdibano.
Xa kuthethwa ngesihloko samalungu eNdibano, iKomishoni yakhetha amalungu ePalamente yaseWales (okanye iWMP), kodwa ukhetho lweMWP lwafumana inkxaso enkulu kwintetho yoluntu.
Kubonakala ngathi amalungu eNdlu ayacebisa ezinye iindlela, kodwa umzabalazo wokufikelela kwisivumelwano unokubangela ukuba umongameli weNdlu, uElin Jones, afumane i-bill malunga notshintsho kwiiveki ezimbalwa.
Umthetho wenguqu uza kubandakanya ezinye iinguqu ezinxulumene nokusebenza kweNdibano, njengemithetho yokukhupha amalungu eNdibano kunye noyilo lwenkqubo yeekomiti.
Amalungu eNdlu aya kuba nelizwi lokugqibela kumbuzo wokuba abizwe njani xa exoxa ngomthetho.
