Omabini la mabandla akhiwa ngamabandla amhlophe ngaphambi kokuba iHarlem ibe sisixeko esikhulu esinomnyama: i-Metropolitan Community ngo-1870 kunye ne-San Martin emva kweminyaka elishumi.
