Ngowe-1939, umlilo washiya isakhiwo sonakele kakhulu yaye, ngoxa ababingeleli bakaBawo Johnson babesenza izicwangciso zokwakha kwakhona, nabo bacela ukuba kwenziwe i-carillon.
