Ngokutsho kweendaba zasekuhlaleni, ingulube yahlasela yaza yabulala umfuyi kwimarike ekumzantsi-ntshona weTshayina.
Le ndoda, ekuthiwa nguYuan, yafunyanwa ifile inesifo esinyukayo, igutyungelwe ligazi kufuphi nelitye lentengiso yaseLiupanshui, kwiphondo laseGuizhou, njengoko iphephandaba iSouth China Morning Post labika ngeCawa.
NgoMeyi 30, 2005, umfuyi wehagu ulungiselela ukufaka iintsholongwane kwiingulube ze-powder eXining, kwiphondo laseQinghai, eChina.
Kubonakala ngathi wahamba nomzala wakhe esuka kwiphondo elingummelwane laseYunnan ngoLwesithathu ukuze athengise iihagu ezili-15 kwimarike.
Ngentsasa elandelayo, umzala wakhe wamfumana efile waza wafumanisa ukuba umnyango womngxunya owawukufutshane wawuvulekile.
Wathi kwakukho ingulube enkulu eyayisemlonyeni wayo.
Uhlolisiso lwezobugwenxa luqinisekisile ukuba ingulube enobunzima obuziikhilogram ezingama-250 yayihlasele umfuyi yaza yafa, ngokutsho kwengxelo.
"Iinyawo zomzala wam zazingafi zize zityumze", watsho umzala, ogama lakhe linguWu, kwiThe Guiyang Evening News.
Umfanekiso weekhamera zokhuseleko ubonisa uYuan engena kwimarike ngoLwesine ngo-4:40 ukuze atye iihagu zakhe.
Umzimba wakhe wafunyanwa malunga neyure kamva.
Isilwanyana esabulala umntu sasingayiyo kaYuan okanye kwisalamane sakhe.
Umphathi wentengiso waxelela iThe Evening News ukuba le ngulube yavalwa ukuze ingahlaseli nabani na omnye, ngoxa amapolisa ayeqokelela ubungqina kuloo ndawo.
Kubonakala ngathi usapho lukaYuan kunye nabasemarikeni basebenzisana ukuze bafumane imbuyekezo ngokufa kwakhe.
Nangona ziyinqambi, asiqali ukuhlaselwa ngumntu yingulube.
Ngo-2016, enye ingulube yahlasela ibhinqa nomyeni walo kwifama yabo eMassachusetts, ishiya indoda ilimele kakhulu.
Kwiminyaka elishumi ngaphambili, ingulube enobunzima obuziikhilogram eziyi-295 yabetha umfama kwi-tractor yakhe de umfazi wayo wayesoyika le nkomo.
Emva kokuba iinkomo zetyetyelwe eOregon ngo-2012, enye ingulube yaseManitoba yaxelela iCBC News ukuba iinkomo azihlali zihlasela, kodwa igazi linokusebenza njengento ebulala abantu.
