Iintaba zeRosa ziza kushiya imvula enkulu kumzantsi-ntshona weUnited States.
Njengoko bekucingelwe kwangaphambili, iRosa iya buthathaka njengoko isasazeka phezu kwamanzi abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Nangona kunjalo, uRosa uza kunikela imvula eninzi kumantla eMexico nakumazantsi-ntshona eUnited States kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo.
URosa wabangela umoya owawuqhuba ngeekhilomitha eziyi-136 ngeyure, isivuthuvuthu esingu-1 ukususela ngeCawa ukuya kutsho ngentsimbi yesihlanu kusasa (ngexesha laseMpuma) yaye wawusondele kwiikhilomitha eziyi-620 kumzantsi-ntshona wePunta Eugenia (eMexico).
Kulindeleke ukuba uRosa ahambe aye emantla ngeCawa.
Okwangoku, kuLwandlekazi iPasifiki, kuqalise ukuvela uxinzelelo oluphantsi, oluhamba ngasempuma ukuya kwiNtshona ye-US. Njengoko uRosa esondela kwiNhlonhlo yaseBaja California ngoMvulo, isaqhwithi esishushu siya kuqalisa ukuqhubela phambili imvula eshushu eshushu eshushu eshushu emantla, kumzantsi-ntshona we-US.
URosa uza kushiya ngaphezu kwe-25 yeesentimitha zemvula kwezinye iindawo zaseMexico ngoMvulo.
Ekugqibeleni, xa imvula etshisayo idibana noxinzelelo oluphantsi olusondelayo, kuya kubakho imvula enamandla ngokubanzi kumazantsi-ntshona kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo.
Kwindawo ethile, phakathi kwe-2 ne-10 yeesentimitha zemvula ziya kubangela izikhukula eziyingozi, ukugeleza kwenkunkuma, nokudumba kwentlango.
Iimvula ezishushu ezishushu ziya kubangela imvula ephantse ibe ziisentimitha ezi-5 ukuya kwezi-8 ngeyure kwiindawo ezithile, ingakumbi kumazantsi eNevada naseArizona.
Kumanqanaba asezantsi-ntshona, ingakumbi kwilizwe laseArizona, kulindeleke imvula engamasentimitha amahlanu ukuya kweyi-10.
Ngenxa yemvula ehlaselayo, kusenokwenzeka ukuba kubekho izikhukula ezikhukhula ngokukhawuleza.
Ngenxa yoko kusongela imvula enkulu, akucetyiswa ukuba uhambe entlango.
Imvula enamandla inokujika imingxunya ibe yimilambo enamaqhekeza yaye izaqhwithi ziya kubangela imimoya enomsindo namafu othuli.
Ukucinezeleka okuphantse kufike kuza kushiya imvula eninzi kwiindawo ezithile zonxweme olusemazantsi eCalifornia.
Izantyalantyala zemvula zinokushiya amanzi aphantse abe ziisentimitha ezimbini, nto leyo enokubangela ukuba kubekho umonakalo omncinane, nto leyo enokwenza iindlela zibe ziinkangala.
Le yayiza kuba yimvula yokuqala enenkungu kweli candelo ngexesha lonyaka.
Ezinye izantyalantyala zomoya ezihlakazekileyo ziya kuqala ukuza eArizona ngentsimbi yokugqibela yangeCawa nangentsimbi yokuqala yangoMvulo, ngaphambi kokuba imvula iqale ekupheleni koMvulo nangoLwesibini.
Imvula enamandla iza kutsala iCowers Quarters ngoLwesibini nangalo lonke uLwesithathu.
Ngo-Oktobha, kuya kubakho utshintsho olukhulu kubushushu eU.S. ngenxa yokutshisa kwee-Arctic nokufudumala kwamazwe ashushu.
Maxa wambi, oku kubangela utshintsho olukhulu lobushushu kumgama omfutshane.
Umzekelo omhle wale mahluko obushushu ngulo uza kwenzeka kumbindi we-US ngeCawa.
Kuya kubakho umahluko ophakamileyo we-7 degrees phakathi kweKansas City, eMissouri, neOmaha, eNebraska, neSt. Louis neDes Moines, eIowa.
Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo, ubushushu obude behlobo buza kuzama ukubuyela kwimeko yabo buze buqhubeke buqhubeka.
Kwiindawo ezininzi ezikwindawo emaphakathi nasempuma yeUnited States, kuqale u-Oktobha efudumeleyo, yaye amaqondo obushushu aya kuba ngama-26 degrees ukusuka kumzantsi weLwandlekazi ukuya kwiindawo ezisemantla mpuma.
NgoLwesibini, iNew York inokufumana ubushushu obufikelela kuma-26 degrees, obungaphezulu kwe-12 degrees.
Isibikezelo sethu sexesha elide sibonisa ukuba kuya kubakho amaqondo obushushu angaphezulu komlinganiselo kwimpuma ye-US kwisiqingatha sokuqala sika-Oktobha.
