Kwakhona kwabakho ukudibana kwiiyure kamva kwaye amapolisa asebenzisa amaqhinga ukuze athintele umlo.
Kangangeeyure ezininzi, amaqela ahlukeneyo, eneembono ezinjengokuthi ni olvidado ni perdón, ajongana nababhikishi bama-unionists ekhwaza esithi Viva España.
Abantu abali-14 banyanyekelwa ngenxa yokwenzakala okuncinane ngexesha leemvukelo, ngokweendaba zasekuhlaleni.
Iingxabano zisaqhubeka zisezingeni eliphezulu kule ngingqi kunyaka emva kokuvota ngo-Oktobha 1, okubhalwe ngokungekho mthethweni eMadrid, kodwa kwenziwa ngamaCatalan ahlukeneyo.
Abavoti bakhetha inkululeko ngenani elikhulu, nangona abantu ababandakanyekayo babengenamdla, kuba abantu abachasene nokuhlukana babhokota kakhulu.
Ngokutsho kwamagosa aseCatalan, phantse abantu abayi-1 000 balimala kunyaka ophelileyo emva kokuba amapolisa ezame ukuthintela ukuvota kwiitafile zokhetho kulo lonke elo mmandla, apho kwabakho ukungqubana okunogonyamelo.
Amaqela axhasa ulawulo oluzimeleyo ahlala ngoLwesihlanu ebusuku ukuze aphephe umboniso wokuxhasa amapolisa aseKhaya.
Lo mbutho waqhubeka, kodwa wanyanzelwa ukuba athathe indlela eyahlukileyo.
UNarcis Termes, oneminyaka engama-68, umqhubi wombane owayesenza umlo wokwahlukana nomfazi wakhe wathi akanathemba lokuba iCatalonia iza kuba lilizwe elizimeleyo.
Kulo nyaka uphelileyo, sasiphila ixesha elimnandi.
Ndabona abazali bam bekhala ngenxa yokuvota, kodwa ngoku siphazamisekile, utshilo.
Nangona bephumelele ngempumelelo ebalulekileyo, nangona incinane, kunyulo lwengingqi ngoDisemba ophelileyo, amaqela asePro Catalan alwa nzima ukuze agcine inkqubela kulo nyaka, njengoko iinkokeli zawo ezininzi ezaziwayo, nokuba ziziindlalifa okanye zivalelwe, zilinde ukugwetywa ngenxa yendima yazo ekucwangciseni iresiphi nakwisibhengezo senkululeko.
UPuig, umenzi-mveliso oneminyaka engama-42 ubudala, owathatha umyalezo wefowuni yakhe waza wafaka umyalezo wezi ziganeko ezenziwa ngamapolisa, wathi le ngxabano yaqaliswa ngabezopolitiko kumacala omabini.
Uthi: "Kukho izinto ezininzi ezibangela ukuba abantu bangakwazi ukuzibamba.
NgoMgqibelo, uOriol Junqueras, omnye weenkokeli ezisithoba zaseCatalan ezivalelwe entolongweni ukususela ekupheleni konyaka ophelileyo, wabhengeza ukuba uza kuthatha inxaxheba kunyulo lwePalamente yaseYurophu kunyaka ozayo.
Ukulwela ukhetho lwaseYurophu yeyona ndlela ilungileyo yokugxeka ukubuyela umva kwimigaqo-siseko yentando yesininzi kunye nokugxekwa esiye sabona kuRhulumente waseSpeyin, utshilo.
