Ukuhlaselwa nguMenga kunika uLivingston uloyiso olungu-1-0 kwiRanger
Igoli yokuqala kaDolly Menga kwiLivingston yaqinisekisa uloyiso
U-Livingston owenziwe ngcono wahlaba umxhwele iRangers ngokufumana ukulahleka kwesibini kuSteven Gerrard kwimidlalo eli-18 njengomqeqeshi weqela lase-Ibrox.
UGary Holt wakhuphuka ngomnye umkhosi, waza uHibernian waba ngowesibini.
Kulo nyaka, iGerrard ayikaze iphumelele ngaphandle kwekhaya kwaye ngeCawa ezayo iya kudibana neHearts, ezikhokelayo kwibhodi ngamaphuzu asibhozo.
I-Ranger iza kufumana i-Rapid Vienna ngoLwesine kwi-Europa League.
Okwangoku, iLivingston yandisa umda wayo wokuphumelela kwiqela ukuya kwimidlalo emithandathu.
ULivingston udlula amathuba phambi komntu obonakala enamandla
Iqela likaHolt laliza kuba linyathelo elingaphambili ngaphambi kokuba lifumane amanqaku, nto leyo eyabangela zonke iintlobo zeengxaki kwiRanger ngenxa yomdlalo wabo othe ngqo.
UScott Robinson wadlula ekuvikeleni kodwa waphoswa ngumgcini-mnyango, emva koko uAlan Lithgow wadutyulwa emva kokungena ukuze agqibezele umgangatho we-Craig Halkett phambi komgcini-mnyango.
Iqela elibanjweyo lalinelisekile ngokuvumela iRanger ukuba idlale phambi kwabo, lisazi ukuba banokubangela iingxaki kwiindwendwe ngokudlala ibhola.
Ngaloo ndlela kwafika injongo egqibeleleyo.
I-Rangers yabanika umpu wamahhala kwaye u-Livingston wafuna ukungena, kunye nomdlalo odibeneyo ka-Declan Gallagher no-Robinson kuMenga, owabetha ibhola waza wafaka umgomo ukusuka embindini wendawo.
Ngelo xesha, iRanger yayilawula indawo, kodwa yayingenakukwazi ukudlula ekuvikeleni umamkeli weqonga kwaye umgcini-mnyango, uLiam Kelly, wayeluxolo.
Lo mdlalo waqhubeka de kwayinyanga yesibini, nangona uAlfredo Morelos wamnqanda uKelly.
UAllan McGregor, umgcini-mnyango weRanger, walahla isibheno sikaScott Pittman, waza uLithgow wahlala kude nomnye umqhubi kaLivingston.
Kwiindawo zaseLivingston kwakusoloko kungena abantu abahamba ixesha elide kodwa bekusoloko kungena abantu abahamba kakuhle.
Izinto eziphawulekayo zeLivingston (uhlalutyo)
UAlasdair Lamont weBBC Scotland kwibala laseTony Macaroni
Umdlalo obalulekileyo kunye nesiphumo esihle kwiLivingston.
Bonke abantu bathi badlala umdlalo omhle kakhulu, kodwa waqhubeka ewenza waphumelela.
Indlela yakhe yokudlala kunye nesampulu yakhe ayitshintshanga kangako ukususela ekunyukeni kwakhe, kodwa oku kubangelwa kakhulu nguHolt ngendlela aye waqinisa ngayo iqela ukususela ekufikeni kwakhe.
Wayenamaqhawe amaninzi.
UHalkett, owayengumphathi weqela, wayemkhulu yaye ekhokela ukhuselo olulungelelaniswe kakuhle, ngoxa uMenga egcina uConor Goldson noJoe Worrall bephaphile ngalo lonke ixesha.
Kodwa ke, iRanger yayingenalo ithemba.
Nangona babeba nemihla emihle noGerrard, abazange baphumelele.
Abazange bakwazi ukuzibophelela, kuba bafika kwintsimi echasene nabo kanye, nto leyo ekwenza baqaphele ukuba iRanger ibekwe phakathi kwetafile.
U-Erdogan wamkelwa kakuhle eCologne
NgoMgqibelo, ngoSeptemba 29, kwakukho uncumo nesibhakabhaka esiluhlaza ngexesha lesidlo sakusasa seenkokeli zaseTurkey naseJamani eBerlin.
Usuku lokugqibela lohambo oluphikisayo lukaMongameli uErdogan eJamani, ngenjongo yokubuyisela ubudlelwane phakathi kwamaqabane e-NATO.
Babeneengxoxo malunga nemibandela efana namalungelo oluntu, inkululeko yeendaba kunye nokujoyina kweTurkey kwi-EU.
Emva koko, uErdogan waya eCologne ukuze avule umzi-mzi omtsha omkhulu.
Esi sixeko sinabantu abaninzi abangamaTurkey ngaphandle kweTurkey.
Amapolisa athi kukho izizathu zokhuseleko zokuthintela abantu abangama-25 000 ukuba bangadluli phambi kwecawa, kodwa abaninzi babemanyene ukuze babone umongameli wayo.
Kwakhona kwavakala amakhulu abachasi baka-Erdogan, abaninzi babo bengamaKurd, abagxeka zombini imigaqo-nkqubo ka-Erdogan kunye nesigqibo sikaRhulumente waseJamani sokumamkela kweli lizwe.
Ezi ziganeko zibonisa indlela ekwahlukana ngayo le ndwendwe, eyamkelwa njengeqhawe ngamaJamani aseTurkey ize ithathwe njengabantu abazenzekelayo ngabanye.
Ingozi yemoto eDeptford: Umkhweli webhayisekile usweleka emva kokungqubana nemoto
