Le ngozi yenzeka emva kokuba omnye umqhubi webhayisekile esweleke emva kokugqitywa yimoto eyabaleka eChilders Street, phantse iikhilomitha ezimbini ukusuka kwindawo yenzondo ngoMgqibelo.
