I-Long Lartin Prison: Amagosa amathandathu esetyhula emva kweemvukelo
Amagosa amathandathu entolongo akhubazekile xa kwabakho ingxabano entolongweni yamadoda, ngokutsho kolawulo lwepenitenti.
Iimbambano zaqala kwiNtolongo yaseLong Lartin, eWorcestershire, malunga ne-9:30 ngeCawa yaye zisaqhubeka.
Iingcali zeqela eliphambili (elibizwa ngokuba yi Tornado) zilawula ukuphazamiseka, apho kubandakanyeka abantu abasibhozo abangaphakathi kwaye oku kuchaphazela iphazili.
Amagosa afumana uncedo ngenxa yokwenzakala ebusweni kwindawo.
Isithethi seNtolongo sithi: "Abasebenzi abakhethekileyo beentolongo baye bathunyelwa ukuze bajongane nale ngxaki iqhubeka kwiNtolongo yaseLong Lartin.
Abasebenzi abathandathu baye bancedwa ngenxa yokwenzakala.
Iintolongo zethu azibekezeleleki ubundlobongela yaye siyacacisa ukuba abo banembopheleleko baya kubekwa ezandleni zamapolisa kwaye banokuchitha ixesha elingakumbi bevalelwe.
Ijele laseLong Lartin likhaya lamabanjwa angaphezu kwama-500, kuquka amanye amabanjwa anobungozi kakhulu kweli lizwe.
NgoJuni kwaxelwa ukuba umphathi wejele wafumana uncedo lwezonyango emva kokuba igosa elivalelweyo limhlasele.
Ukongezelela, ngo-Oktobha wonyaka ophelileyo, kwacelwa amagosa okuphikisana nemvukelo ukuba aye entolongweni ukuze ajongane nengxabano enzulu apho kwahlaselwa abasebenzi bepenitenari ngeebhola zebhiliyoni.
I-Hurricane Rose isongela iPhoenix, eLas Vegas naseSalt Lake City ngamanzi aqukuqelayo (iindawo ezomileyo zinokuxhamla)
Akuqhelekanga ukuba kubekho uxinzelelo lweemvula ezishushu eArizona, kodwa oko kanye kunokwenzeka ekuqaleni kweveki ezayo xa amaqhezu okugqibela e-Hurricane Rose ewela intlango esemazantsi ntshona, esengozini yezikhukula ezitshitshisayo.
I-National Weather Service sele ikhuphe izilumkiso zamanzi angakhange avuswe ngoMvulo nangoLwesibini kwintshona yeArizona, emazantsi nasempuma yeNevada nakumazantsi mpuma eCalifornia naseUtah, kuquka izixeko zasePhoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas naseSalt Lake City.
Kulindeleke ukuba uRosa aye ngqo ePhoenix ngoLwesibini, eshiya imvula ekupheleni koMvulo.
I-National Meteorological Service yasePhoenix yathi kwi-tweet nje kuphela ezilishumi zeenkanyamba ziye zahlala zikwimeko yesiphepho esishushu okanye isifo esinamandla kumgama weekhilomitha ezingama-321 ukusuka ePhoenix ukusukela ngo-1950.
Ngowe-1967, inkanyamba uKatrina yasondela kwiikhilomitha eziyi-65 ukusuka kumda waseArizona.
Iimodeli zakutshanje zeNational Hurricane Center zibonise imvula enenkanyamba yeesentimitha ezi-5 ukuya kweziyi-10 ezinokunyuka ziye kwiisentimitha ezili-15 kwiindawo ezizimeleyo zeMogollon Escarpe, eArizona.
Kusenokwenzeka ukuba imvula inokuba ziisentimitha ezi-2 ukuya kwezi-5, ize ifike kwi-10 kwiindawo ezisemagqagaleni nakwezinye iindawo ezisemzantsi ntshona weli hlane, kuquka iintaba ezimi ngeentaba neGrand Basin.
Kwiindawo ezingenazo izikhukula, imvula yeRosa inokujongwa njengentsikelelo, kuba loo mmandla ufikelwa yimbalela.
Nangona ukhukhula luyinto enzulu, kusenokwenzeka ukuba imvula eninzi inenzuzo ngenxa yeemeko ezomileyo ezenzeka ngoku kumzantsi-ntshona.
Ngokutsho kweUnited States Drought Monitor, ngaphezu kwe-40% yeArizona inembalela, ubuncinane, yembalela enkulu, inqanaba lesibini eliphezulu, njengoko kwaxelwa kwi weather.com.
Okokuqala, indlela eya kuhamba ngayo iRosa iza kubetha inhlonhlo yaseBaja California eMexico.
URosa, onamandla okudubula ngentsasa yangeCawa, owenza iiyure eziyi-136 ngeekhilomitha, ukuma iikhilomitha eziyi-619 kumzantsi wePunta Eugenia, eMexico, yaye uqhuba umgama ongamakhilomitha ayi-19 ngeyure ukuya emantla.
Le nkanyamba ifumana amanzi abandayo kwiPasifiki, ngoko iyaphela.
Ngoko ke, kulindeleke ukuba iqhwithi elinamandla laseMexico lifike ngoMvulo emva kwemini.
Kunokuba nemvula eninzi kwiindawo ezithile eMexico, nto leyo ebangela ukuba kubekho izikhukula.
Iimvula ezinamandla ezinobunzima obuphakathi kwe-7 ne-15 yeesentimitha ukusuka eBaaja California ukuya kumantla-ntshona eSonora, zinokuba ziisentimitha ezingama-25, njengoko kuxelwe kwi-weather.com.
Emva koko, iRosa iza kuqhuba ukuya emantla eMexico njengesaqhwithi esishushu, ngaphambi kokuba ifike kumda waseArizona ngentsimbi yokuqala yosuku lwangoLwesibini njengesifo esishushu.
IZiko Lehlathi Lezonyango LaseMerika lithi, "Ingozi enkulu yeRosa okanye izidumbu zayo yimvula enenkanyamba eBaja California, kumantla ntshona eSonora nakumazantsi ntshona entlango yaseMerika".
Le mvula kulindeleke ukuba ibangele izikhukula eziyingozi ezingalindelekanga nokugcwala kwengxangxasi entlango, kwakunye nokuduma komhlaba kwiindawo ezisezintabeni.
Ukuhlaselwa eMidsomer Norton: Abanoosisi abane babanjwe ngokuzama ukubulala
