UKavanaugh wafakaza phambi kweCongress ngoLwesine, ekhanyela ngokuqinileyo nangovelwano isityholo sikaChristine Blasey Ford sokuba wayemxhaphazile ngokwesondo kumashumi eminyaka eyadlulayo xa ayesengumntwana.
UFord naye wanikela ubungqina kule ntlanganiso.
