UMongameli wenza iingxelo ezingachananga malunga nokhetho lukaKavanaugh xa ethetha ngokubaluleka kokuthatha inxaxheba kweRiphabliki kunyulo lwexesha eliphakathi.
Kusele iiveki ezintlanu ngaphambi kokhetho olubalulekileyo ebomini bethu.
Andizibonakalisi, kodwa ngumsebenzi, utshilo.
