Ivoti yokuqala ebalulekileyo yeNkundla yoWiso-mthetho ekumiselweni kukaKavanaugh kulindeleke ukuba yenziwe kungekudala ngoLwesihlanu, uxelele i-CNN isikhulu esiphezulu senkampani yeRiphablikhi.
Amakhulu abantu asweleka kunyikima nakutsunami eIndonesia, inani liya lisanda
Ubuncinane abantu abangama-384 baye bafa, abaninzi behlelwa ngamaza amakhulu athwele amabhishi emva kwenyikima enkulu ne-tsunami kwisiqithi sase-Indonesia iSulawesi, njengoko kwaxelwa ngamapolisa ngoMgqibelo.
Abantu abaninzi babedibene ukuze babhiyozele umsitho kwibhishi yasePalu ngoLwesihlanu xa amaza afikelela kwiimitha ezintandathu ezinyuka ayefika kunxweme xa kwakuhlwa, esusa abaninzi ekufeni aze atshabalalise yonke into.
I-tsunami yenzeka emva kwenyikima enamandla angama-7.5.
Xa izolo kwaqikelelwa ukuba kunokubakho i-tsunami, abantu babesechibini kwaye abazange babaleke ngoko nangoko, ngoko baba ngamaxhoba, utshilo uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi se-Indeonesia National Agency for Disaster Management (BNPB) kwintlanganiso yeendaba eYakarta.
UNugroho uthi, "Itsunami ayizange ifike yodwa, yahlutha iimoto, imithi, izindlu, yatshayela yonke into esemhlabeni".
Wongezelela ukuba abanye abantu baye bakhwela emithini ukuze baphephe itsunami baza basinda.
Abantu abamalunga ne-16,700 baye bafudukela kwiindawo ezingama-24 ePalu.
Iifoto zeenqwelo moya ezipapashwe yi-arhente zabonisa ukutshabalala kwezakhiwo ezininzi nevenkile, amabhulorho aphulileyo, kunye nomzi oqhelekileyo.
Iimbombo zomoya zazisoloko zihlasela isixeko esiselunxwemeni ngoMgqibelo.
Olu ngxubusho lweenyikima lwavakala kwindawo eyayinabantu abazizigidi ezingama-2,4
I-BPPT (Bureau for the Evaluation and Application of Technology) yachaza kwisikhumbuzo sayo ukuba amandla akhutshwa yinyikima enkulu eyayenzeke ngoLwesihlanu ayiphindwe ngama-200 kunalawo aphuma kwibhombu yeathom eyayiphose eHiroshima kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Wongezelela ukuba indawo yesixeko, esemazantsi entlambo ende, inokuba yayibonisa ubungakanani be-tsunami.
UNugroho wachaza umonakalo njengento enkulu, wathi amawaka amakhaya, izibhedlele, iziko lokuthenga neehotele zabhidlika.
Uthi izidumbu zabanye abantu ababethwele ezi ziko zafunyanwa phantsi kweenkunkuma zezakhiwo eziwileyo, abantu abangama-540 balimala baza abangama-29 babekho.
UNugroho wathi inani labantu ababuleweyo kunye nomonakalo unokuba mkhulu kwiikhilomitha ezingama-300 zonxweme olusemantla ePalu, indawo ebizwa ngokuba yiDonggala, esondele kakhulu kwincopho yenyikima.
UGugroho uthi, "Iinkcukacha zokuba uDonggala ulapho azizange zibonakale".
Abantu abangaphezu kwe-300 000 bahlala apho, utshilo uMnqamlezo Olubomvu kwisikhumbuzo, wongezelela ukuba abasebenzi bawo namavolontiya baya kwiindawo ezichaphazelekayo.
Uthi: "Kodwa oku kunokuba yintlekele, kodwa kunokuba kubi nangakumbi".
NgoMgqibelo, eli sebe lafumana ukugxekwa kakhulu ngokungachazi ukuba i-tsunami ibethe iPalu, nangona abasemagunyeni bathi amaza sele efikile kunxweme xa kwakukhutshelwa isilumkiso.
Kwividiyo ethathwe ngumntu othanda ukuzonwabisa yaza yabelwana ngayo kwii-social media, umntu othile osesitezi sokugqibela esisakhiwo usiva abantu abasesitratweni besithi kuza kubakho i-tsunami.
Kungekapheli nemizuzu, udonga lwamanzi lufika kunxweme, luye lutshabalalise izakhiwo neemoto.
I-Reuters ayizange ikwazi ukuqinisekisa le nto kwangoko.
Inyikima ne-tsunami zabangela ukuba kubekho ukucima okukhulu kwezinto ezibangela ukuba kungabikho unxibelelwano phesheya kwePalu, nto leyo eyayenza kube nzima ukuba abasemagunyeni balungelelanise umsebenzi wokukhulula abantu.
Abasemagunyeni bathi umkhosi uqalise ukuthumela iinqwelo-moya ezithwala izinto eziphuma eYakarta nakwezinye izixeko, kodwa abantu abafudukayo basadinga ukutya nezinye izinto eziyimfuneko.
Isikhululo seenqwelo-moya esixekweni sivulelwe imisebenzi yokunceda kuphela kwaye siza kuvalwa kude kube ngu-Oktobha.
UMongameli Joko Widodo uhleliwe ukutyelela amaziko okufuduka kaPaul ngeCawa.
