UJohn Edward: Izakhono zolwimi zibalulekile kubemi behlabathi
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zineendlela ezibalaseleyo zemfundo eziye zaqhubeka ngo-2018 kunye nezinye iziphumo ezibalaseleyo kwiimviwo eziqiniswa yimpumelelo nganye kunye nehlanganisiweyo ezivunyiweyo kwimimandla yezemidlalo, ubugcisa, umculo kunye nezinye iiprojekthi zoluntu.
Ngaphezulu kwama-30 000 abafundi eScotland, ezi zikolo, zimelwe yiBhunga leZikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland (SCIS) zizama ukubonelela ngomgangatho ophezulu wenkonzo kubafundi nakubazali.
Iikholeji ezizimeleyo zijolise ekulungiseleleni abafundi bazo ukuba baqhubeke nemfundo ephakamileyo, kwimisebenzi abayikhethayo nakwindawo abahlala kuyo njengabemi behlabathi.
Njengomsebenzi wemfundo onokwakha nokuqalisa inkqubo yokufunda efanelekileyo, iilwimi zanamhlanje zisaqhubeka ziyinto ethandwayo nezifunwa kakhulu kwizikolo.
Kanye njengokuba uNelson Mandela watshoyo: "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi alwaziyo, umyalezo ufikelela entloko yakhe.
Xa uthetha naye ngolwimi lwakhe, uya kufikelela entliziyweni yakhe.
Esi sisikhumbuzo esinamandla sokuba, ukuba ufuna ukwakha ubudlelwane nokuthembela kubantu bezinye iintlanga, akunakuthembela kwisiNgesi kuphela.
Xa sijonga iziphumo zakutshanje zovavanyo lwangoku, sinokubona ukuba iilwimi ziphezulu kakhulu kwiitheyibhile zokugqwesa, kuba amazinga aphezulu okuphumelela kwizikolo ezizimeleyo.
Lilonke, abafundi abangama-68% abafunda iilwimi zasemzini bafumana amanqaku aphezulu, u-A.
Idatha eyanikwa kumaziko angama-74 ase-SCIS ibonisa ukuba abafundi abangama-72% bafumana i-A kwisiMandarin, ngoxa abangama-72% abafunda isiJamani, abangama-69% abafunda isiFrentshi kunye nama-63% abafunda iSpanish nabo befumana i-A.
Oku kubonisa ukuba izikolo zaseScotland ezizimeleyo zixhasa iilwimi zasemzini kuba zizijonga njengezakhono ezibalulekileyo eziya kufunwa ngabantwana nolutsha ngokuqinisekileyo kwixesha elizayo.
Namhlanje, iilwimi zibonwa njengezifundo ezifanayo nezifundo ze-CTIM (inzululwazi, iteknoloji, ubunjineli kunye nemathematika) kwizicwangciso zokufunda ezikolweni ezizimeleyo nakwezinye iindawo.
Uphando olwenziwe ngo-2014 yiKomishoni yezeMisebenzi nezezakhono yase-United Kingdom lubonisa ukuba, kwizizathu abazinikezayo abaqeshi malunga nobunzima bokufumana imisebenzi, i-17% ibhekisela ekusweleni kweelwimi.
Ngoko ke, ukukwazi ukuthetha ulwimi kuya kusiba yinto ebalulekileyo ukuze ulutsha lungene kumsebenzi olandelayo.
Amathuba omsebenzi afunekayo afuna iilwimi aya esanda, ngoko ke ezi zakhono zibalulekile kwihlabathi eliguqukayo.
Enoba ukhetha uphi umsebenzi, ukuba ufunde ulwimi lwesibini, uya kuba nempumelelo yokwenene kwixesha elizayo ngenxa yokhuphiswano olunjalo, oluya kuhlala ubomi bakho bonke.
Ukukwazi ukunxibelelana ngqo nabantu abavela kumazwe angaphandle kuya kumenza akwazi ukuphumelela ngokuthe ngqo.
Ngokutsho kophando olwenziwe nguYouGov kubantu abadala base-UK abangaphezu kwe-4000 ngo-2013, ama-75 ekhulwini abo babengathethi naluphi na ulwimi lwasemzini kakuhle ngokwaneleyo ukuba banxibelelane.
Ngenxa yoko, ukutyala imali ekufundiseni iilwimi kubalulekile kubantwana banamhlanje.
Ukuba abantwana bayazi iilwimi ezininzi, ingakumbi ezo zezoqoqosho olusaphuhlayo, baya kuba nezixhobo zokunandipha amathuba angcono okufumana umsebenzi oncomekayo.
EScotland, zonke izikolo ziya kufundisa iilwimi ezahlukeneyo.
Amanye amaziko aza kugxininisa kwiilwimi zakudala zanamhlanje, ngoxa amanye aza kufundisa iilwimi ezijongwa njengezibalulekileyo e-UK ngo-2020, ezifana nesiMandarin okanye isiJapan.
Kungakhathaliseki ukuba yintoni na umntwana ayifunayo, esikolweni esizimeleyo unokuzikhethela iilwimi ezininzi ezifundiswa ngabafundisi-ntsapho abaqeqeshiweyo.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zenza konke okusemandleni ukubonelela ngemeko yokufunda elungiselela abantwana kwaye ibaxhobise ngezakhono ezifunekayo ukuze baphumelele, kungakhathaliseki ukuba yintoni eza kwenzeka kubo.
Okwangoku, akukho nto inokuyiphikisa into yokuba, kwimeko yeshishini jikelele, iilwimi zisaqhubeka zibaluleke kakhulu kwikamva lelizwe, ngoko ke oku kufuneka kubonakaliswe kwimfundo.
