I-North Korea ithi akukho ndlela yokuba baqale balahle izixhobo zabo ngokwahlukileyo ukuba abanalo ithemba
NgoMgqibelo, umphathiswa wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea waxelela iZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ukuba ukuqhubeka kwezi meko kwakwenza abantu baseMerika bangathembi yaye kwakungekho ndlela yokuba ilizwe lakhe lilahle izixhobo zenyukliya ngokwahlukileyo phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo.
URi Yong Ho wathi kwiNdibano yeNgqungquthela yeZizwe ngezizwe yonyaka ukuba iNyakatho Korea ithathe "amanyathelo abalulekileyo okwenza izinto ezilungileyo" kunyaka ophelileyo, njengokuyeka ukuvavanya izixhobo zenyukliya nezikrweqe, ukuchitha izakhiwo zokuvavanya izixhobo zenyukliya nokuzibophelela ekungasasazekeni kwezixhobo zenyukliya nakwitekhnoloji yenyukliya.
Noko ke, asikafumani mpendulo efanayo evela eUnited States, utshilo.
 Ukuba asithembani eUnited States, asinakuthembela kukhuseleko lwethu lwesizwe, kwaye, phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo, akukho ndlela yokuba siqale siwulahle ngokungenamthetho
Nangona uRi ephindaphinda izikhalazo ezaziwayo zaseMntla Korea ngokumelana neWashington nefomula yokulwa ne-nuclear ngamacandelo aya kuvuza ilizwe njengoko lithatha amanyathelo ngokuthe ngcembe, isitatimende sakhe sibalulekile, kuba akazange aphinde aphakamise ukulwa ne-nuclear unilateral, njengoko iPyongyang yenzile ngaphambili.
URi wathetha ngesibhengezo esihlangeneyo esenziwe nguKim Jong Un noDonald Trump emva kwentlanganiso yokuqala phakathi komongameli waseMerika osebenzayo kunye nenkokeli yaseMntla Korea ngoJuni 12 eSingapore, xa uKim wazibophelela ekusebenzeni ukuze 'ukususwa kwamachiza kwintshona yeKorea' kwaye uTrump waqinisekisa ukhuseleko lwaseMntla Korea.
I-North Korea iye yafuna ukuphelisa ngokusemthethweni iMfazwe yaseKorea yowe-1950-53, kodwa iUnited States ithi iPyongyang kufuneka iyeke izixhobo zayo zenyukliya ngaphambi kokuba ifike.
Kwakhona, iWashington iye yachasana nezicelo zokuthambisa izigwebo zamazwe ngamazwe kwiNyakatho Korea.
I-United States iye yafuna ukuyeka ukwenza izixhobo zenyukliya kuqala yaza yandisa uxinzelelo ngezo zityholo ukuze iphumelele injongo yayo ngendlela enyanzelisayo, kuquka nokuchasa isibhengezo sokuyeka imfazwe, utshilo uRi.
 Ingcamango yokuba isohlwayo sinokusenza siwele emadolweni ngabantu abangasaziyo.
Ingxaki kukuba ukuqhubeka kwezi ngxaki kuya kusiqinisa ngakumbi ukungazithembi kwethu.
URi akazange athethe ngezicwangciso zeengqungquthela ezimbini zikaKim noTrump, ezazityhilwa ngenyameko yinkokeli yaseMerika kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo ekuqaleni kweveki.
Kunoko, lo mphathiswa wagxininisa iintlanganiso ezintathu ezenziwa nguKim kunye noMongameli Moon Jae waseMzantsi Korea kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo, waza wongezelela wathi: "Ukuba uMzantsi Korea ubulandela umgaqo-nkqubo wokurhoxisa izixhobo zenyukliya endaweni yeUnited States, ukurhoxiswa kweenqwelo-moya ezisemhlabeni kwiphondo laseKorea bekungayi kuba semngciphekweni onjalo".
Nangona kunjalo, ithoni yentetho kaRi yahluke kakhulu kunyaka ophelileyo, xa wathi kwiNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo ukuba kwakungenakuphepheka ukujolisa imijukujelwa yaseMntla Korea kumhlaba waseMerika emva kokuba uMongameli ongendawo uTrump, owayesenza umsebenzi wokuzibulala, ebize uKim ngokuthi "indoda yamarokethi".
Kulo nyaka kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo, uTrump, owathi kunyaka ophelileyo wayesongela 'ukutshabalalisa ngokupheleleyo' uMntla Korea, wadumisa uKim ngesibindi sakhe ekuqhubeleni phambili ekuhlaziyweni izixhobo, kodwa wathi kusekho umsebenzi omninzi ekufuneka wenziwe kwaye kufuneka uqhubeke nokusebenzisa izohlwayo de uMntla Korea ungene kwinto enobungozi.
NgoLwesithathu, uTrump wathi akukho xesha libekiweyo: "Singazithatha iminyaka emibini, iminyaka emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintlanu, akunandaba".
