ISixeko seZokhuseleko siye safaka izigwebo ngokuvumayo kuMntla Korea ukususela ngo-2006, sisenza iinzame zokunciphisa imali ekhokelwa kwiinkqubo ze-ballistic missile neyanyukliya yasePyongyang.
UPompeo wathetha noRi ngaphandle kweNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo waza kamva wathi uza kuphinda atyelele iPyongyang kwinyanga ezayo ukuze alungiselele intlanganiso yesibini.
UPompeo sele etyelele eMntla Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa uhambo lwakhe lokugqibela aluzange lube luhle.
