Abafundi baseHarvard benza ikhosi yokufumana ukuphumla okwaneleyo
Ngenxa yenkqubo entsha efundiswa kulo nyaka kwiYunivesithi yaseHarvard, abafundi baseyunivesithi balala ngakumbi ukuze balwe nenkcubeko yesini esandayo yokufunda ubusuku bonke besela i-caffeine.
Omnye uprofesa wafumanisa ukuba abafundi baseyunivesithi yokuqala ehlabathini badla ngokungazi ukuba banakunyamekela njani abantu.
UCharles Czeisler, onguprofesa wezokwelapha zokulala kwiHarvard School of Medicine, kunye nengcali kwiBrigham and Women's Hospital bayile ikhosi, ekukholelwa ukuba yayiyeyokuqala kwiklasi yayo eUnited States.
Isizathu sakhe sokuqalisa le khosi savela emva kokuba ethethe ngendlela ukungalali kakuhle okuchaphazela ngayo ukufunda.
Ekupheleni kweklasi, enye intombazana yeza kum yaza yabuza ukuba kutheni isandul' ukuva ngale nto, kunyaka wayo wokugqibela.
Uthi akukho mntu wakha wamxelela ngokubaluleka kokulala, nto leyo eyandothusayo, utshilo kwiThe Telegraph.
Le khosi, eyaqala kulo nyaka, ichaza iingcamango ezisisiseko zendlela imikhwa elungileyo yokulala encedisa ngayo kwimpumelelo yezemfundo nemidlalo, ukongeza ekuphuculeni impilo ngokubanzi.
UPaul Barreira, onguprofesa wezifo zengqondo kwiSikolo saseHarvard sezoNyango kunye nomlawuli olawulayo weenkonzo zempilo zekholeji, wathi le yunivesithi yagqiba kwelokuba ifake ikhosi emva kokufumanisa ukuba abafundi balele phantse iveki.
Ikhosi yeyure ibandakanya uthotho lwemisebenzi enxibelelanayo.
Kwisekhondi enye, kukho umfanekiso wegumbi lokulala, apho abafundi becofa kwiikomityi zekofu, kwizikrini, kwiimbadada zemidlalo nakwiincwadi ezibaxelela ngemiphumo yecaffeine nokukhanya, kunye nefuthe lokungalali kakuhle kwimisebenzi yezemidlalo nokubaluleka kokwenza umjikelo wokulala.
Kwelinye icandelo, abathathi-nxaxheba bafundiswa ngendlela ukungalali ixesha elide okunokubandisa ngayo umngcipheko wokuhlaselwa yintliziyo, ukuhlaselwa sisifo sephepha, ukudandatheka nomhlaza.
Emva koko, umfanekiso-ngqangi wekhampasi onemifanekiso esebenzisanayo ukhuthaza abahlanganyeli ukuba bacinge ngemisebenzi yabo yemihla ngemihla.
Siyazi ukuba akuyi kutshintsha indlela yokuziphatha yabafundi ngoko nangoko.
Noko ke, sikholelwa ukuba banelungelo lokwazi, kanye njengokuba nabani na enelungelo lokwazi ngemiphumo yempilo yokutshaya icuba, wongezelela uProfesa Czeisler.
Uthi inkcubeko yokuzingca ngokuchitha ubusuku bephaphile isekho, yaye wongezelela ukuba iteknoloji yanamhlanje noxinzelelo olukhulayo abafundi abajamelana nalo lubonisa ukuba ukungalali kakuhle kuyingxaki ekhulayo.
Ukulala ngokwaneleyo nokulala kakuhle kufanele kube sisikhali esifihlakeleyo kubafundi ukuze balwe noxinzelelo, ukukhathala, nokukhathazeka; kwanokuba ukuze baphephe ukuzuza ubunzima, kuba ukungalali kwenza ingqondo ibe nendlala, ngoko bafuna ukutya ngalo lonke ixesha.
URaymond So, umCalifornia oneminyaka eli-19 ubudala ofunda ibhayoloji yemichiza neyomzimba, wanceda uProfesa Czeisler ekuyileni ikhosi emva kokuya kwelinye lamagumbi akhe okufundela kunyaka ophelileyo kunyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.
Uthi le khosi yamvulela amehlo yaza yamkhuthaza ukuba ayandise ikhampasi.
Uthe eli nyathelo lilandelayo kukucela bonke abafundi abaphumelele kwizikolo eziphakamileyo ukuba bagqibe inkqubo efanayo ngaphambi kokuba bangene kwisikolo esikhuphisanayo.
Uprofesa Czeisler uthi abafundi mabacinge ngokufaka i-alamu xa belala baze bavuswe, baze bazi ukuba ukukhanya okwesibhakabhaka okukhanya kwizikrini zezinto zombane ne-LED kunokubangela ukuba baphazamiseke.
Livingston 1 - Rangers 0: Injongo kaMenga ingcwaba amadoda kaGerrard
