I-Ibrox yayifuna ukufumana impumelelo yayo yokuqala ngaphandle kwekhaya ukususela ngoFebruwari 4-1 eSt. Johnstone, kodwa iqela likaGary Holt lahlulwa nguGerrard okwesibini kwimidlalo eli-18 njengomqeqeshi, lishiya iqela lakhe lilinamaphuzu asibhozo kwiHearts, iinkokeli zeLadbrokes Premiership.
