Kwakufanele ukuba bafumane umlinganiselo wemizuzu emibini yokuqala, xa uMenga wafaka umngxunya kwindawo kaScott Pittman owawela phakathi komkhosi, emshiya yedwa phambi kuka-Allan McGregor, kodwa umlinganiswa wasemaphandleni wamkhupha.
UKeaghan Jacobs wakhupha i-fault enzulu kwi-Captain Craig Halket, kodwa umhlobo wakhe ekuhlaleni, uAlan Lithgow, wakwazi ukumthumela ngaphandle kuphela ngomthi omde.
I-Ranger yafumana ulawulo, kodwa kwakubonakala ngathi kukho ithemba elingaphezulu kokukholelwa kumdlalo wabo kwisithathu sokugqibela.
Ngokuqinisekileyo uAlfredo Morelos waziva enetyala ngomzuzu we-15 womdlalo, xa yena noSteven Lawless badibana, kodwa umphathi uSteven Thomson waba zizithulu kwisicelo somColombian.
I-Rangers yafumana amaqhosha amabini okufaka umnyango kwisiqingatha sokuqala, kodwa umlindi wangaphambili we-Ibrox, uLiam Kelly, wayengenangxaki yokujongana nentloko kaLassana Coulibaly kunye nokuphosa okudinayo kuka-Ovie Ejaria.
Nangona umgomo owanikwa iLivingston ngomzuzu wama-34 wawungavisisani nento eyayicingwa, akukho mntu unokukhanyela ukuba bawufanelekele lo mzamo.
Kwakhona, iRanger ayizange ikwazi ukujamelana nokudlula kukaJacobs.
