Umjovo omtsha womhlaza unokufundisa inkqubo yomzimba ukuba ibone iiseli ezinobungozi
Umjovo omtsha womhlaza unokufundisa inkqubo yomzimba ukuba ibulale iiseli ezinobungozi.
Njengenxalenye yonyango, iyeza lifundisa inkqubo yomzimba ukuba ibone iiseli ezinobungozi.
Le ndlela ifuna ukuba kususwe iiseli zomzimba kumguli zize zonakaliswe elebhu.
Ngoko banokufumana iprotheni eqhelekileyo kwiintsholongwane ezininzi baze bayenze kwakhona.
Uvavanyo lwezazinyo luvelisa iziphumo ezithembisayo kwizigulana ezinomhlaza ohlukeneyo.
Ibhinqa elalinotyando, elifundisa inkqubo yokuzikhusela ukuba ihlolisise iiseli ezinobungozi, labona umdlavuza walo wesibeleko usiya ushabalala kangangeenyanga ezingaphezu kwe-18.
Le ndlela ifuna ukuba kususwe iiseli zomzimba kumguli zize ziguqulwe kwilebhu ukuze zikwazi ukubona iprotheni eqhelekileyo kwiintsholongwane ezininzi, ebizwa ngokuba yiHER2, ize ihlale iiseli.
UProfesa Jay Berzofsky we-US National Cancer Institute eBethesda, eMaryland, wathi: "Iziphumo zethu zibonise ukuba sinento ethenjisiweyo yokugonya".
UProfesa Berzofsky wathi, i-HER2  ikhuthaza ukukhula kweentlobo ezahlukeneyo zomhlaza, njengomhlaza webele, weqanda, womoya okanye womhlaza we-colorectal.
Indlela efanayo yokuthatha iiseli zomzimba zabaguli baze babafundise ukuhlasela iiseli ezinomhlaza iye yasebenza kunyango lweentlobo ezithile zeengcongconi.
