UJohnny English: Ukuphinda uthathe inyathelo.
Ngoku sele sele sele kuyinto eqhelekileyo ukukhangela i-Brexit kwiifilimu ezintsha ezinendlela yaseBritane. Kubonakala ngathi oku kuyafana nokwenza kwesi siqendu sitsha se-action and comedy parody franchise uJohnny English, owaqala ngo-2003 noJohnny English waza wabuya ebomini ngo-2011 noJohnny English Returns.
Ngaba le ngxelo ingenangqiqo yokuba singamaxhoba angekho ngqiqweni yindlela entsha esiyithumela ngayo kumazwe angaphandle?
Nangona kunjalo, uJohnny English ongenakuziqonda, onamehlo akhe agxekayo nobuso obungachazekiyo, uye wavuselela ilayisensi yakhe yokungena umlenze okwesibini.
Ewe kunjalo, ngumlindi oyimfihlelo ongahlambulukanga, nangona enamaqhinga angavamile okuchitha umtsalane, kodwa enento encinane kaClouseau, intetho kaMnu. Bean, kunye ne-snipe enjalo, eyayidlala inotshi enye kumxholo weMoto ezivulwayo kwiMidlalo yeOlimpiki yaseLondon 2012.
Ukongezelela, ekuqaleni kwakusekelwe kumntu ongaziwayo, ohamba ngamazwe, owayedume kwiminyaka emininzi edluleyo nguAtkinson kwiibhengezo zeTV zeBarclaycard, ezenza ukuba kubekho ingxolo.
Kule nxalenye yokugqibela, kukho ixesha elinye okanye amabini amnandi.
Ndandikuthanda ukubona uJohnny English esondela kwi-helicopter enxibe iimpahla zeminyaka yeeNkulungwane ZaseMandulo njengoko iinqwelo-moya zantlitheka kwinqwelo.
I-Atkinson's gift for physical comedy iyabonakala, kodwa imvakalelo yehlaya iyacotha kwaye iyasebenza, ingakumbi ngoku xa ii-movie ze-series ezifana ne-007 kunye ne-Mission Impossible zongeza izithako ezihlekisayo ngaphandle kwengxaki.
Umtsalane ubonakala ubhekisela kubantwana kunakubantu abadala, yaye kum, iingozi zikaJohnny English ezingenangqondo azikho zilungelelaniswe kakuhle njengamahlaya ka-Atkinson athule njengoMnu. Bean.
Ngoku, ingxoxo ephindaphindiweyo yangoku kukuba iBritani ikwiingxaki ezinzulu.
I-hacker iye yangena kwi-network ye-super secret ye-espionage yase-UK, ityhila iinkcukacha zabo bonke abasebenzi bayo abasebenzayo ngenxa yokudandatheka kwe-agent esebenzayo, indima encinci enzima kuKevin Eldon.
Eli lilinzi elizalisa iglasi yeNdunankulu, umlinganiswa onobuchule nonobunzulu obona ukuthandwa kwakhe kwezopolitiko kuncipha: uEmma Thompson wenza konke okusemandleni akhe kulo mlinganiswa ufana noTheresa May, kodwa isicatshulwa asishiyi ncam indawo yokusebenza.
Abacebisi bakhe bokuphengulula bayaxelela ukuba ekubeni zonke iintlola ezikhoyo zisengozini, kuya kufuneka athathe umntu ozikhuphe.
Le ndoda imele ibe nguJohnny English, ngoku ofundisa kwisikolo esiyingozi, nangona enikela iiklasi ezingaqhelekanga zokuba ngumlindi wezemfihlo: kukho amahlaya amnandi, kuba iyikholeji yokungcebeleka efana neSikolo seRocke.
UEnglish udluliselwa eWhitehall kwintlanganiso engxamisekileyo aze adibane nomhlobo wakhe omdala uBough, owakhelwa nguBen Miller kwakhona.
Ngoku, uBough ngumyeni otshatileyo onomphathi wenqanawa encinane, indima entle engazisebenzisi kakuhle uVicky Pepperdine.
Ngoko, iBatman noRobin abenza izinto ezimbi kakhulu kwiSecret Service kaMongami babuyela kwisenzo, kunye nomfazi omhle nobulalayo uOphelia Bulletova, odlalwa nguOlga Kurylenko.
Okwangoku, intloko yelizwe iyawela ezandleni zendoda enezigidi zezigidi ezithandwayo kwilizwe lezobugcisa ethi inokusombulula iingxaki zeekhompyutha zaseBritani: uJason Volta, odlalwa nguJake Lacy.
U-English noBough baqala i-odiseya yabo yeemeko ezingenangqondo: bazenza ababhaki, batshisa indawo yokutyela yaseFransi, bakhupha ingxolo befihla kwi-yacht yaseVolta; ukongeza, u-English uba yintlekele xa ezama ukusebenzisa i-shell ye-virtual reality ukuze aziqhelanise nendawo yangaphakathi yendlu kaVolta.
Ngokuqinisekileyo, basetyenziswa ngokupheleleyo kweso siganeko sokugqibela, kodwa, nokuba sinomtsalane kangakanani na, iseti isasaza imvakalelo encinane.
Umkhiqizo oqhelekileyo.
