NgoMgqibelo, iNew York iza kubamba iGlobal Citizen Festival, umnyhadala womculo wonyaka, apho iqela elikhulu leenkwenkwezi lihlanganisana ukuze lihlangane kwintshumayelo efanayo: ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu ehlabathini.
Kulo nyaka, kwiSikhumbuzo seSixhenxe, iGlobal Citizen Festival iza kubona indlela amashumi amawaka abantu aza kuhamba ngayo kwiGreat Lawn yaseCentral Park ukuze bonwabele imiboniso kaJanet Jackson, uCardi B noShawn Mendes, kodwa ukuze baqaphele injongo yokwenene yale mbhiyozo: ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu buka-2030.
I-Global Citizen Festival, eyaqala ngo-2012, yandisa i-Global Poverty Project, iqela lokufundisa ngamazwe elithemba ukuba liza kuphelisa ubuhlwempu ngokunyusa inani labantu abazama ukulwa nalo.
Ukuba ufuna ukufumana ithikithi yasimahla kumsitho (ngaphandle kokuba ungakwazi ukuhlawula ithikithi le-VIP), ababekho kwiikonsathi kuye kwafuneka bagqibezele uthotho lwemisebenzi okanye izenzo, njengokuvolontiya, ukuthumela ii-imeyile kumlawuli wehlabathi, ukwenza umnxeba okanye nantoni na enye enceda ekuboniseni abantu ukuba banomdla kwinjongo yabo yokuphelisa ubuhlwempu.
Kodwa yintoni eyenziwe yiGlobal Citizen kwiminyaka eli-12 emva kokufikelela kule njongo?
Ngaba le ngcamango yokuvuza ngomculo wasimahla yindlela yokwenene yokukhuthaza abantu ukuba bathathe amanyathelo okanye ngaba yindlela nje yokubiza amagama ngokuthi "ukuhlanganisana", okubizwa ngokuba yindawo esiyiyo xa sicinga ukuba senza into eluncedo ngokwenene xa sisayina isicelo se-intanethi okanye sithumela i-tweet?
Ukususela ngo-2011, iGlobal Citizen ithi ibhale ngaphezulu kwe-19 yezigidi "zento" zabasekeli bayo ezixhasa iinjongo ezininzi ezahlukeneyo.
Ngenxa yezi zenzo, bathi baye bafumana iinkokeli zehlabathi ukuba zivakalise izibophelelo nemigaqo-nkqubo exabisa ngaphezu kweedola ezingama-37 bhiliyoni, eza kuchaphazela ubomi babantu abangaphezu kwe-22.5 bhiliyoni ngo-2030.
Ekuqaleni kuka-2018, iqela lacaphula izibhambathiso nezibhengezo ezingama-390 ezivela kwizabelo zalo, apho, sele kuhlawulwe okanye kuqokelelwe ubuncinane i-10 yezigidigidi zeedola.
Iqela lichaza ukuba imali eqinisekisiweyo iye yachaphazela abantu abamalunga ne-649 yezigidi ehlabathini lonke.
