"Ngenxa yenkxaso karhulumente wase-UK, abaxhasi, oorhulumente basekhaya kunye nabasebenzi beGlobal Citizens njengawe, sinokubeka umda omncinane kwimbali yokungekho sikweni kwezentlalo ngenxa yokungondleki, utshilo uTracey Ullman, ummeli we "The Power of Nutrition", kwisihlwele ngexesha lekonsathi ngo-Aprili 2018 eLondon.
Eli qela laphinda lathi, emva kokuba liye laphumeza amanyathelo angaphezu kwama-5 000 okuzama ukuphucula ukutya e-UK koomama nabantwana, urhulumente wabhengeza inkxaso-mali yeprojekthi, iPowwer of Nutrition, apho amabhinqa nabantwana abazizigidi ezi-5 baya kuxhamla kuncedo olunxulumene nokutya.
