Amazwe ali-18 neD.C. axhasa umngeni wokufumana umgaqo-nkqubo omtsha wesigxina
Amazwe ali-18 kunye neSithili saseColumbia axhasa isibheno senkundla kumgaqo-nkqubo omtsha waseMerika wokulahla ukukhuselwa kwamaxhoba abakhuselayo kubundlobongela basekhaya okanye amaqela.
Abameli bamazwe ali-18 kunye nezithili babhalisa "ngobuhlobo" ngoLwesihlanu eWashington ukubonisa inkxaso yabo kumntu ofuna ukukhuselwa ojamelene nomyalelo wangoku, kubika i-NBC News.
Ummangali akazange atyhilwe ngegama lakhe elipheleleyo kwityala elithi "Grace v. Sessions" elaqhutywa yi-ACLU ngo-Agasti ngokumelana nemigaqo-nkqubo ye-federal.
Wathi umhlobo wakhe "noonyana bakhe, abangamalungu eqela elinabantu abanogonyamelo", bamxhaphaza, kodwa amagosa aseMerika amgatya isicelo sakhe sokukhuselwa ngoJulayi 20.
Wabanjwa eTexas.
Amagqwetha amele la mazwe amele uGrace achaza iEl Salvador, eHonduras neGuatemala, ezivelisa izicelo ezininzi zokufumana isazelo e-US, njengeentlanga ezijongene neengxaki eziqhelekileyo ezinxulumene nogonyamelo lwasekhaya kunye namaqela eqela.
Umgaqo-nkqubo omtsha we-asylum wase-US uphinde wasusa isigqibo sango-2014 esenziwe yiBhunga Lezikhalazo Zokufudukela Kwamanye Amazwe (BIA) sokuba abafuduki abangenayo imvume yokusaba ngenxa yobundlobongela basekhaya banokufaka isicelo sokusabela kweli lizwe.
UMtshutshisi-Jikelele weSithili saseColumbia, uKarl Racine, wenza izitatimende ngoLwesihlanu esithi lo mgaqo-nkqubo mtsha "uyaziphosa phandle iminyaka emininzi yomthetho wamazwe ngamazwe, wefederal nowaseburhulumenteni".
'Ngokwemithetho yelizwe, zonke izicelo zokusabela kufuneka zigwetywe ngenxa yeenkcukacha nemeko ethile yombandela, kodwa oku kuphambuka kuloo mgaqo,' itsho njalo i-amicus curiae.
Kwakhona, amagqwetha abonisa ukuba imigaqo-nkqubo yokwala ukungena kwabangena kwamanye amazwe iyingozi kuqoqosho lwase-US kuba athi basoloko baba ngoosomashishini kwaye "bafuna umsebenzi ofunekayo".
UMtshutshisi Jikelele uJeff Sessions wayalela abagwebi abahamba ngeemfuduko ukuba bangaboneleli ngodongwe amaxhoba abaleka ukuxhatshazwa kwasekhaya nobundlobongela bamaxhoba ngoJuni.
"Abantu abashiya amazwe abo ngenxa yokutshutshiswa okanye ukusongelwa ngenxa yohlanga, unqulo, ubuzwe okanye ukuba yinxalenye yeqela elithile loluntu okanye imbono ethile yezopolitiko banokufaka isicelo sokusabela", watsho uSessions xa wayethetha ngesi sikhokelo ngoJuni 11.
I-asylum ayizange yenziwe njengendlela yokunciphisa zonke iingxaki, okanye zonke iingxaki ezinzulu, abantu abajamelana nazo imihla ngemihla kwihlabathi liphela.
