Ummeli waseMerika utyhola iChina ngokuba "nemibono ephosakeleyo" "ngentengiso"
Kwiveki emva kokuba iphephandaba laseTshayina eliyiofisi epapashwe kwisakhiwo esinemaphepha amane kwiphephandaba laseMerika apho kwakukhuthazwa khona iinzuzo zorhwebo phakathi kwe-US ne-China, ummeli wase-US e-China watyhola iBeijing ngokusebenzisa amajelo eendaba aseMerika ukusasaza intetho yakhe.
NgoLwesithathu ophelileyo, uMongameli waseMerika uDonald Trump wathetha ngesongezelelo sentlawulo yeChina Daily kwiDes Moines Register, iphephandaba elithengisa kakhulu eIowa, emva kokumangalela iChina ngokufuna ukuphazamisa ukhetho lweCongress yaseMerika ngoNovemba 6, into echaswa ngokucacileyo yiChina.
Isityholo sikaTrump sokuzama kukaBeijing ukuphazamisa ukhetho lwaseMerika sabonisa oko amagosa aseMerika akuchaza kwiReuters njengesigaba esitsha kumkhankaso okhulayo owaqaliswa nguWashington wokunyanzelisa uxinzelelo eChina.
Nangona kuqhelekile ukuba oorhulumente bamanye amazwe bapapashe iintengiso zokukhuthaza imisebenzi yabo yorhwebo, iBeijing neWashington ngoku zivalelwe kwidabi lokurhweba elikhulayo eliye labakhokelela ekunyuseni amanqanaba eencitho kwamanye amazwe kuwo omabini amacala.
Iirhafu ezihlawulelayo zaseTshayina ezazisebenza ekuqaleni kwemfazwe yorhwebo zazenzelwe ukuthumela kumazwe angaphandle kumazwe afana neIowa, axhasa iRiphabliki kaTrump, ngokweengcali zaseTshayina nezaseMerika.
UTerry Branstad, onguNjengele waseMerika eChina nowayesakuba nguRhuluneli waseIowa, ongomnye wabathengisi abakhulu beemveliso zezolimo eChina, wathi iBeijing iye yaba yingozi kubasebenzi baseMerika, kubalimi nakubashishini.
Njengoko uBranstad wabhala kwinqaku lakhe leDes Moines Register ngeCawa, iChina "iyandisa loo ngcinezelo ngokupapasha iintengiso kwiphepha lethu elikhululekileyo".
"Ukuzama ukusasaza intetho yabo, urhulumente waseTshayina usebenzisa inkcubeko yaseMerika yenkululeko yokuthetha nenkululeko yeendaba xa ezama ukupapasha isaziso esihlawulwayo kwiDes Moines Register", wabhala watsho uBrandstad.
"Ekupheleni koko, kwi-kiosk yasesitalatweni apho silapha eBeijing, kubonakala nje amazwi ambalwa angavaniyo kwaye akukho mboniso wokwenene weembono ezingafaniyo abantu baseTshayina abanokuba nazo malunga nendlela echaphazelekayo eqhubeka ngayo uqoqosho lwelizwe labo, kuba amajelo eendaba alawulwa yingcinezelo eqinileyo yeCawa yamaTshayina", wabhala.
Wongezelela wathi "enye yeephephandaba eziphambili zaseTshayina ayizange ifune ukupapasha" inqaku layo, nangona engazange achaze ukuba yeyiphi.
Abahlalutyi bathi amaRiphablikhi aya ezama ukuzikhupha kwizimvo zabesifazane ngaphambi kokuvota kwesiqingatha sesigxina kunye nokudumba kukaKavanaugh
Ekubeni amaRiphablikhi amaninzi adumileyo evala imigca yawo ukuze alwele umviwa weNkundla ePhakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh ngenxa yezityholo ezahlukeneyo zokuhlaselwa ngokwesondo, abahlalutyi baye balumkisa ukuba kusenokubakho ukubuyela umva, ngokukodwa ngabafazi, kwivoti ezayo ezenzeka phakathi kwekota.
Iimvakalelo ezikule meko ziye zaba namandla kakhulu kwaye baninzi amaRiphablikhi abaye babonisa ukuba bafuna ukuqhubeka nokuvota.
"Kwezi ntlobo zemicimbi akukho ndlela yokubuyela umva", watsho uGrant Reeher, onguprofesa wezeNzululwazi ngezepolitiki kwiSikolo saseMaxwell kwiYunivesithi yaseSirakusa, kwiThe Hill kwinqaku elapapashwa ngoMgqibelo.
UReeher uthi akathandabuzi ukuba uzama kutshanje kukaSenator Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ukuxhasa uphando lwe-FBI kulungile ukuzola abavoti abangenamdla kulo mbandela.
"Abafazi abayi kulibala oko kwenzekayo izolo; abayi kulibala ngomso okanye ngoNovemba", watsho njalo uKarin Jean-Pierre, umcebisi omkhulu nesithethi sesizwe seqela eliqhubela phambili iMoveOn, ngokwephephandaba laseWashington, D.C.
NgoLwesihlanu ekuseni, ababhikishi abahlanganisene eminyango yeSenate babethetha "November is coming!" (uNovemba uza kufika kungekudala!) xa amaRiphabliki alawula iKomiti yezoBulungisa agqiba kwelokuba aqhubeke nokumiswa kukaKavanaugh, nangona ubungqina bukaDkt Christine Blasey Ford, njengoko ingxelo yeMic.
UStu Rothenberg, ongengomntu onyanzelisayo kwezopolitiko, uthi: "Inzondelelo nentshukumisa yamaDemocrat ayibonakali".
"Abantu bathi impembelelo sele ibalulekile, ibe kunjalo.
Kodwa isenokuba nkulu ngakumbi, ingakumbi phakathi kwabafazi abangenakuzincama abahlala emaphandleni nabavoti abancinane, abaneminyaka eli-18 ukuya kweli-29, abangathandiyo ukuvota nokuba umongameli uyabathanda".
Kwanangaphambi kokuba uFord anike ubungqina obungakumbi malunga nezityholo zakhe zokuxhatshazwa ngokwesondo kumviwa weNkundla Ephakamileyo, abahlalutyi bathi kusenokwenzeka ukuba kubekho ukubuyela umva ukuba amaRiphablikhi aqhubeka nokuqinisekisa.
"Le ngxaki iye yaba yingxaki enkulu kwiqela lamaRiphablikhi", watsho uMichael Steele, owayesakuba ngumongameli weKomiti yeSizwe yamaRiphablikhi, ekuqaleni kweveki ephelileyo, njengoko kubikwe yiNBC News.
"Akusekho nto nje kuphela yokuvota kwequmrhu okanye yokuvota kokugqibela, nokuba bahleli ebhentshini kaKavanaugh; kukwakhona nendlela amaRiphablikhi aye aphatha ngayo konke oku nendlela aye amnyamekela ngayo", utshilo uGuy Cecil, umlawuli wePriorities USA (iqela elinceda ekunyulweni kwamaDemokhrasi).
Noko ke, amaMerika abonakala ehlukene phakathi; ayazi ukuba amele akholwe ngubani emva kobungqina bukaFord noKavanaugh, nangona bambalwa abanye abaye bamxhasa.
Uhlolisiso olutsha lwe-YouGov lubonisa ukuba ama-41% abantu abaphenduliweyo bakholelwa ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi ubungqina bukaFord, ngoxa ama-35% athi akholelwa ngokuqinisekileyo okanye mhlawumbi kuKavanaugh.
Ngaphezu koko, ama-38% athi akholelwa ukuba, ngokuqinisekileyo okanye ngokuqinisekileyo, uKavanaugh uxokile ebudeni bobungqina bakhe, ngoxa ama-30% athi okufanayo ngoFord.
Emva kokunyusa kukaFlake, i-FBI ngoku iphenya ingxelo kaFord, kunye nezinye iingxelo zomnye ummangali, uDeborah Ramirez, iThe Guardian yazisa.
UFord wafaka ubungqina phantsi kwesifungo kwiKomishoni yezoBulungisa yeSenate kwiveki ephelileyo waza wathi uKavanaugh wamxhaphaza enxilile eneminyaka eli-17 ubudala.
Kwangaxeshanye, uRamirez uthi umviwa weNkundla Ephakamileyo wambonisa amalungu akhe esini xa wayeseYale ngeminyaka yee-1980.
Umvelisi weWebhu yeHlabathi lonke uceba ukuqalisa i-Intanethi entsha ukuze akwazi ukhuphisana neGoogle neFacebook
UTim Berners-Lee, owasungula iWebhu yeHlabathi, usungula inkampani entsha ezama ukuncintisana neFacebook, iAmazon neGoogle.
I-Inrupt yeyona projekthi yokugqibela kwi-legend ye-tech, inkampani esekwe kwiqonga likaBerners-Lee elivulekileyo.
I-Solid ivumela abasebenzisi ukuba bakhethe ukuba bayigcina phi idatha yabo kwaye ngoobani abaza kuba nokufikelela kuluphi ulwazi.
Kwi-interview ekhethekileyo ne-Fast Company, uBerners-Lee wadlala esithi injongo ephambili ye-Inrupt "kukulawula ihlabathi".
"Kufuneka kube ngoku", watsho malunga startup.
"Lilixesha lembali".
Le app isebenzisa itekhnoloji kaSolid ukuze abasebenzisi bakwazi ukudala "ugcino lwedatha yobuqu kwi-intanethi" okanye i-POD.
Unokuba noluhlu, uluhlu lwemisebenzi engaphambi kokuqhutywa, ikhalenda, ithala leengoma nezinye izixhobo zobuqu nezobungcali.
Kunjengokuba iGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack neSpotify zonke zifumaneka kwisikhangeli ngaxeshanye.
Into ekhethekileyo ngokugcina idatha yobuqu kwi-intanethi kukuba umsebenzisi nguye owenza isigqibo sokuba ngubani onokufikelela kuluhlobo luni lolwazi.
Le nkampani ibiza oku ngokuthi "ukuqeqesha abantu ngokusebenzisa idatha".
Ngokutsho kukaJohn Bruce, umlawuli-jikelele wenkampani, injongo ye-Inrupt kukufaka izixhobo, iinkqubo nezakhono ezifunekayo ukuze iSolid ifikelele wonke umntu.
Okwangoku, inkampani ibunjwa nguBerners-Lee, uBruce, iqonga lokhuseleko elithengwe yiIBM, abanye babaphuhlisi ababandakanyekileyo abaqeshwe ukuba basebenze kule projekthi kunye noluntu lwabaprogram abazinikeleyo.
Ukususela kule veki, abaphuhlisi bezobuchwepheshe ehlabathini lonke banokuzenzela iiapps zabo ezingasetyenziswayo ngezixhobo ezikhoyo kwiwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
UBerners-Lee uthi yena neqela lakhe abathethi "noFacebook noGoogle malunga nokuba baya kuvelisa utshintsho olukhulu okanye hayi apho zonke iimodeli zabo zeshishini ziguqulwa ngokupheleleyo imihla ngemihla.
"Asiyi kucela imvume".
Kwiphepha-ndaba leMedium ngoMgqibelo, uBerners-Lee wabhala ngo-Inrupt ukuba "umsebenzi wayo kukubonelela ngombane wezorhwebo kunye ne-ecosystem ukunceda ukukhusela ububanzi kunye nomgangatho wewebhu entsha eyenziwe kwiSolid".
Ngowe-1994, uBerners-Lee waguqula i-Intanethi xa waseka iWorld Wide Web Consortium (W3C) kwi-Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kwiinyanga ezidlulileyo, uBerners-Lee uye waba nendima ebalulekileyo kwingxoxo engathathi cala yenethiwekhi.
Nangona sele eqalisa i-Inrupt, uBerners-Lee uya kuhlala engumsunguli kunye nomlawuli weWorld Wide Web Consortium, iWeb Foundation kunye ne-Open Data Institute.
UBerners-Lee wongezelela wathi: "Ndiqinisekile ukuba siza kuba nexesha elifanelekileyo kule web.
UBernard Vann: Umfundisi owafumana uMnqamlezo Wobunqobe kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi I
Umfundisi weCawa yaseNgilani kuphela owafumana uMnqamlezo Wobunqobe kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi I njengomlozi uye wanikwa imbeko kwidolophu yakowabo kwiminyaka eli-100 kamva.
U-Lt. Colonel Reverend Bernard Vann wafumana le mbasa ngoSeptemba 29, 1918 kwi-attack yaseBellenglise naseLehaucourt.
Noko ke, wabulawa ngumdubuli weentolo kwiintsuku ezine kamva, yaye akazange azi ukuba wanikwa imbeko enkulu yemikhosi yaseBritani.
NgoMgqibelo, abazukulwana bakhe ababini bafumana ilitye lesikhumbuzo kwitheko elaliseRushden, eNorthamptonshire.
Omnye wabo, uMichael Vann, wathi "yayinomfuziselo okhethekileyo" yokuba ilitye lafunyanwa kwiminyaka eyi-100 emva kwemfazwe eyabangela ukuba agqoke umkhulu wakhe.
Ngokutsho kweLondon Gazette, ngoSeptemba 29, 1918, uLt. Colonel Vann wakhokela iqela lakhe eSaint-Quentin Canal "ngamaxesha omkhuhlane omkhulu nangaphantsi komlilo omkhulu weengcongolo nemipu".
Emva koko wabaleka waya kumgca womlilo waza, "ngesibindi esikhulu", wabangela ukuba umgca uqhube ngaphambi kokuba afike kumngxunya ngesandla esinye waza wawisa abathathu kwiqela.
U-Lt. Colonel Vann wabulawa ngumdubuli waseJamani ngo-Oktobha 4, 1918, kwinyanga nje emva kokuba imfazwe iphelile.
UMichael Vann oneminyaka eyi-72 wathi izinto ezenziwa ngukayise "zinkulu kangangokuba andisoze ndikwazi ukufikelela kwinqanaba lakhe, kodwa zikhuthaza".
Yena nomntakwabo, uGqr. James Vann, nabo bafaka isithsaba seentyatyambo emva kwembutho, eyayibandakanywe yiBrentwood Imperial Youth Band.
UMichael Vann wathi "lililungelo elikhulu ukuba abe yinxalenye yaloo mboniso" yaye wongezelela wathi "ukungagungqi kweqhawe lokwenene kubonakala xa lixhaswa kangaka".
Abalandeli beMMA bahlala bephaphile ubusuku bonke be-Bellator 206, kodwa babukela kuphela uPeppa Pig
Masithi uhlala ubusuku bonke ujonga yonke iBellator 206 ukuze ekugqibeleni ungavunyelwa ukuba ubukele umsitho oyintloko.
Iphaneli yaseSan Jose yayineengxabano ezili-13, ezintandathu zazo zifakwe kwikhadi eliphambili, kwaye e-UK yayiza kusasazwa bukhoma ebusuku kwi-Channel 5.
Ngentsimbi yesithandathu, kanye njengoko uGegard Mousasi noRory MacDonald babelungiselela ukujamelana, ababukeli base-UK babothuka xa inkqubo yatshintshela kuPeppa Pig.
Abanye abazange bamangaliswe kukuba babesele bephaphile de kube sekuseni kakhulu ukuze babone umlo.
Omnye umlandeli wakhe kwi-Twitter wachaza ukutshintsha kwemifanekiso epopayi "njengengengomdlalo onzima".
"Kukho umthetho karhulumente olawula umxholo osasazwayo ukususela ngo-6:00 yaye wawungalunganga, ngoko kwafuneka batshintshe inkqubo yabantwana", utshilo uDave Schwartz, umongameli ophezulu wezentengiso nezonxibelelwano eBelalator, xa sibuza ngokudluliselwa.
""Khangela ingulube encinane, ewe".
USihlalo weBellator, uScott Coker, uthe baza kuhlengahlengisa inkqubo ukuze babandakanye ababukeli baseBritani kwii-editions ezizayo.
UCoker wathi: "Xa ndicinga ngento enokuyenza xa ndifuna ukuyisasaza, ndicinga ukuba inokusebenza.
"Kodwa ngentsimbi yesithandathu ekuseni ngeCawa, ngoko asikwazi ukuyenza de kube ngeCawa ngexesha lethu, nto leyo eya kuba ngoMvulo kubo.
Sijonge indlela yokuyenza.
Ndikholelwe, xa kwabakho utshintsho, kwafika imiyalezo emininzi, ibe ayingabo bonke ababenobubele.
Sazama ukuyilungisa le nto kuba ekuqaleni sasicinga ukuba le ngxaki yezakhono.
Kodwa ke zange kube njalo.
Ndiyakuthembisa ukuba akusoze kwenzeke kwixesha elizayo.
Siza kuyinciphisa ibe ziintsuku ezintlanu kunokuba zibe zithandathu, nto leyo esiqhele ukuyenza.
Yinto enzima gqitha le".
Desert Island Discs: UTom Daley wayeziva engento yanto ngenxa yesondo lakhe
Umqhubi we-Olimpiki uTom Daley uthi wakhula eziva engekho mgangatho ngenxa yesondo lakhe, nangona oko kwakhokelela ekubeni abe ngumqhubi weqonga.
Xa wayeneminyaka eyi-24, wasixelela ukuba akazange aqonde de wafika esikolweni samabanga aphakamileyo ukuba "abantakwabo bonke babengafani nam".
Kwincwadana yokuqala yeDesert Island Discs yeRadio 4, eboniswa nguLauren Laverne, wathi injongo yakhe xa ethetha ngamalungelo abantu abangamakhwenkwe angamafanasini yayikukuzisa "ithemba" kwabanye abantu.
Kwakhona wasixelela ukuba ekubeni ngutata kwamenza waqala ukungakuxabisi ukuphumelela kwiiOlimpiki.
Umqhubi oqhelekileyo wale nkqubo ingummangaliso, uKirsty Young, uza kuba ephumile kangangeenyanga ezimbalwa ngenxa yokugula.
Kwinto yokuqala kaLaverne, uDaley, owazichaza njengomntu ongenamdla, wathi wayeziva "ephantsi" kwabanye ngexesha lobuntwana bakhe, kuba "ayemkelwa ngokwasentlalweni ukuba uthanda amakhwenkwe namantombazana".
Wathi: "Ude kube namhlanje, loo mvakalelo yokungafani nokuzingca iye yandenza ndafumana amandla namandla okuphumelela".
Wayefuna ukubonisa ukuba "yintoni na", watsho, ngoko akazange adimazeke xa ekugqibeleni wafumanisa ukuba usesini.
Lo mdlali weembasa ezimbini zobhedu kwiiOlimpiki uye waba ngumntu obalaseleyo kwiqela lamaLGBT kwaye umfanekiso wakhe usetyenziswe kwiMidlalo yeCommonwealth kulo nyaka eOstreliya ukuze afune ukuba amazwe amaninzi aphelise ubufanasini.
Wathi wabalisa kuba wayeziva enethamsanqa ngokuphila ngokukhululekileyo, ngaphandle kokuziphindezela, yaye wayefuna ukudlulisela loo "themba" kwabanye abantu.
Lo mdlali wehlabathi wamaxesha amathathu uthi naye wayengumntu othandana nomntu, umenzi wefilimu waseMerika uDustin Lance Black, owaziyo ngo-2013.
UDaley watshata kunyaka ophelileyo nomntu owaphumelela iOscar, oneminyaka engama-20 ubudala, nangona wathi umahluko wobudala awuzange ube yingxaki.
"Xa uphila ixesha elide kangaka ukususela ebutsheni" (waqala ukuya kwiMidlalo yeOlimpiki eneminyaka eli-14 ubudala waza uyise wafa ngumhlaza kwiminyaka emithathu kamva), kunzima ukufumana umntu oneminyaka efanayo naye oye wadlula kwii-ups and downs of you.
Esi sibini saba nomntwana ngoJuni, owathi wabizwa ngokuba nguRobert Ray Black-Daley, kwaye uDaley wathi "imbono yabo yehlabathi" yatshintshile.
"Ukuba bendibuzwe kunyaka ophelileyo, zonke iimpendulo zazinokuba zijikeleze 'ndifanele ndifumane imbasa yegolide,'" watsho.
"Kodwa, khangela! Zininzi izinto ezibaluleke ngakumbi kuneemedali zegolide zeOlimpiki.
Igolide yam yeOlimpiki nguRobbie".
Unyana wakhe ubizwa ngokuba nguRobert, uyise owafa ngo-2011 eneminyaka engama-40 emva kokuba efumene isifo somhlaza wengqondo.
UDaley wathi uyise wayengafuni ukuba afe, yaye enyanisweni, enye yezinto zokugqibela awayezibuza kukuba ngaba babenamatikiti okuya eLondon 2012 kuba wayefuna ukuba kwindawo yokuqala.
"Andikwazanga ukumxelela ukuba andizukwazi ukuba kumgca wokuqala", watsho.
"Wayesidla isandla sakhe phakathi kwesam xa wayeka ukuphefumla yaye akuzange kube yiloo mzuzu kanye apho wayeka ukuphefumla waza wafa ndaqonda ukuba wayengento yokunqandwa", utshilo.
Kunyaka olandelayo, uDaley wancintisana kwiiOlimpiki zika-2012 waza waphumelela imbasa yebrons.
Wathi: "Ngelo xesha ndaqonda ukuba le yayiyiloo nto ndandiyiphupha ubomi bam bonke: ukhuphisana kwiqula phambi kwam ekhaya kwiMidlalo yeOlimpiki, kwakungekho nto ibhetele kunoko".
Oku kwakukwakhokelela ekunyuleni ingoma yakhe yokuqala, Proud kaHeather Small, owamlandela kwisigaba sokulungiselela iMidlalo yeOlimpiki.
I-Desert Island Discs isasazwa kwi-BBC Radio 4 ngeCawa ngo-11:15 BST.
UMickelson, onobuhle obungaphantsi, wahlala ebhentshini kwiRyder Cup ngoMgqibelo
U-Phil Mickelson waseMerika uza kubeka irekhodi ngeCawa xa edlala umdlalo wakhe wama-47 weRyder Cup, kodwa kuza kufuneka atshintshe ifomu yakhe ukuba ufuna ukuphepha ukuba ibe ngumgangatho ombi.
UMickelson, owayedlala kulo msitho wenziwa rhoqo emva kweminyaka emibini ukuze afumane irekhodi okwesi-12 kwelo xesha, wabhangqiswa nguCaptain Furyk kwi-fourballs kunye ne-foursomes ngoMgqibelo.
Kunokuba abe ngundoqo, njengoko eye wazenza kumazwe aseMerika, lo mdlali weyona midlalo mikhulu kangangezihlandlo ezihlanu kwafuneka anelise ukuhlaziya abanye, aze, kwezinye iimeko, azame ukuphucula indlela yakhe yokudlala ukuze akwazi ukuzilungisa izinto ezimcaphukisayo.
Akasoloko engenazintloni, nkqu nakwinqanaba eliphezulu lomsebenzi wakhe, lo mdlali oneminyaka engama-48 ubudala akakho kwimo yakhe entle kwibala leGolf National, apho umqhubi omde eqhubeka esohlwaya ngokuxoka.
Yaye ukuba inkundla ayisekho nzima ngokwaneleyo, uMickelson, kumdlalo wesithoba weCawa, uza kudibana nomntu ophum' izandla kwiBritish Open, uFrancesco Molinari, ojoyine umqeshi wokuqala uTommy Fleetwood ukuze aphumelele imidlalo emine edlalwe kule veki.
Ukuba amaMerika, awayemaphuzu amane ngaphantsi xa aqalisa imidlalo eyi-12, ayeqala ngendlela ebalaseleyo, umdlalo kaMickelson unokuba ngowona ubalulekileyo.
UFuryk wabonisa ukuba uyamthemba umhlobo wakhe, yaye akazange akwazi ukuthetha okuninzi.
UFuryk uthi: "Wandiqonda kakuhle indima endandinayo namhlanje, wandibetha emqolo waza wandijikeleza ngengalo wathi ndiza kulungela ngomso".
"Uzithemba kakhulu.
Uyingcali kwiHolo yeNdumiso yaye uye wanikela kakhulu kula maqela ngaphambi kwale veki.
Mhlawumbi ndandingazi ukuba uza kudlala imidlalo emibini.
Ndandicinga ukuba kuza kubakho okungakumbi, kodwa le yindlela eyaphuma ngayo kwaye yile ndlela esicinga ukuba yayifanele ibe ngayo.
Ufuna ukuba lapho, njengabo bonke abanye".
NgeCawa, uMickelson uza kudlula umda kaNick Faldo wokudlala imidlalo emininzi kwiNdebe yeRyder.
Oku kusenokuba kokugqibela kwimbali yeRyder Cup engazange ikwazi ukuzilinganisa ngokuthe ngqo izinga lomgangatho wayo.
UMickelson unemidlalo eli-18, eli-20 elahlekileyo neyesithandathu, nangona uFuryk wathi ubukho bakhe buye bazisa ixabiso elingenamsebenzi kwiqela.
"Uyonwabisa, uyathuka, unobuchule, uthanda ukuhlekisa ngabanye; kumnandi ukuba naye kwiqela", watsho.
"Ndicinga ukuba abadlali abaselula bayithanda ukuba naye njengenkxaso, kwakhona kule veki; bekumnandi.
Oku kunceda okungaphezulu nje kokudlala".
Umphathi waseYurophu, uThomas Bjorn, uyazi ukuba ubunkokheli bunokuphela kungekudala
UThomas Bjorn, umphathi weYurophu, uyazi kakuhle ukuba, nangona ungena unobangela omkhulu kwiintsuku zokugqibela zeRyder Cup, unokuba ngumdyarho ongathandekiyo.
Lo mDanes wenza umdlalo wakhe wokuqala ngo-1997 eValderrama, apho iqela elikhokelwa nguSeve Ballesteros lalinamathuba amahlanu okuphumelela amaMelika, kodwa ekugqibeleni laphumelela kuphela ngokunyuka iinyawo zabo, liphumelela i-141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Asizami ukukukhumbuza ukuba senze umdyarho omkhulu eValderrama; sakwenza naseBrookline saza salahlekelwa, sakwenza eValderrama saza saphumelela, kodwa kancinci", utshilo uBjorn, oboniswe, emva kokubona isizukulwana sika-2018 siphumelela ngo-5-3 ngoLwesihlanu kwaye izolo sihola nge-10-6 eLe Golf National.
Ibali liza kusifundisa mna nabo bonke abantu ukuba loo nto ayigqityiwanga.
Kufuneka niyinike yonke into ngomso.
Phuma phandle uze wenze oko kufuneka ukwenze.
Oku akupheli de amanqaku abe semgceni.
Sinento esifuna ukuyenza, ukuphumelela esi sigqoko, yaye oko kuphela ekufuneka sicinge ngako.
Ndihlala ndithetha njalo, ndijolise kubadlali abali-12 beqela lethu, kodwa siyazi kakuhle ukuba yintoni elapha, apho bakhona, akukho nto ingaphezulu, akukho nto ingaphantsi, kunabadlali ababalaseleyo ehlabathini".
Enekratshi ngoko kwenziwa ngabadlali bakhe kwintsimi yegalufa enzima, uBjorn wongezelela wathi: "Andifuni ukuqhubeka.
Ngomso ngumceli mngeni ohlukileyo.
Oko kuza kuqala ngomso kukuzibandakanya komntu ngamnye, kwaye oku kwahlukile.
Kuhle ukwabelana ngezinto ezenzekayo nomhlobo wakho xa izinto zihamba kakuhle, kodwa xa ulapho wedwa, uvavanya zonke izakhono zakho njengomdlali wegalufa.
Lo ngumyalezo omele udluliselwe kubadlali, ukuze ufumane okona kulungileyo ngomso.
Ngoku umele umshiye umhlobo wakho, uye uzame ukwenza okulungileyo".
Xa echasene noBjorn, umlingane wakhe uJim Furyk uza kuzama ukwenza abadlali bakhe benze ngcono ngokwabo kunokuba benze njengezibini, ngaphandle kukaJordan Spieth noJustin Thomas, abaqokelela amanqaku amathathu ukuya kwabane.
UFuryk ngokwakhe uye waba kwiimbombo zomibini kwimihla yokugqibela yezo zikhuphiswano zikhulu kwaye wayeyinxalenye yeqela eliphumeleleyo eBrookline kwaye ekugqibeleni waphulukana nalo xa iYurophu yenze "Ummangaliso waseMedinah".
"Ndilikhumbula ilizwi ngalinye", wasitsho xa sabuzwa ukuba uBen Crenshaw, owayengumphathi weqela ngo-1999, wakwazi njani ukukhuthaza abadlali bakhe ngomhla wokugqibela.
"Sineemidlalo ezili-12 ezibalulekileyo ngomso, kodwa kufuneka siqale kakuhle njengoko senzayo eBrookline, njengoko nibona eMedinah.
Xa sonke siqhubela phambili, yonke ingcinezelo iba kuloo maqela aphakathi.
Sachaza isicwangciso sethu saza sabenza baphuma benoluvo lokuba siza kuzama ukwenza into emagqabini ngomso".
UThomas wanikwa umsebenzi wokuzama ukukhokela umlo aze ajamelane noRory McIlroy kumdlalo ophambili, kunye noPaul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood noIan Poulter, abanye baseYurophu kwisiqingatha sesibini seendidi.
"Ndandidla ngokuhamba neqela labafana ngendlela efanayo kuba ndicinga ukuba bahlanganisa yonke indlela", watsho uBjorn malunga nokukhethwa kwakhe ngabanye.
Inqanawa entsha yemfazwe yaseJamani, ehlelwe kwakhona
I-Fregate entsha ye-Navy yaseJamani yayimele ukuba yahlawulwa ngo-2014 ukuze ithathe indawo yeenqanawa ezindala zexesha leMfazwe ebandayo, kodwa ayiyi kwenziwa de kube kunyaka ozayo ngenxa yeenkqubo ezingasebenzi kakuhle kunye nokunyuka ngokuthe ngcembe kweendleko, kwaxelwa ngamajelo asekuhlaleni.
Ukuhanjiswa kwe "Rheinland-Pfalz", inqanawa ekhokelayo kwii-frigates ezintsha zeklasi yaseBaden-Württemberg, ngoku kuye kwacothwa ukuya kwisiqingatha sokuqala sika-2019, njengoko iDie Zeit icaphula izitatimende zomthetheli wasemkhosini.
Inqanawa yayimele ukuba yajoyina iArmada ngo-2014, kodwa iingxaki ezivela emva kokuhanjiswa kwaphazamisa ukugqitywa kweprojekthi enqwenelekayo.
Iinqanawa ezine zeklasi yaseBaden-Wuerttemberg ezifunyenwe nguMkhosi wezasolwandle ngo-2007 ziya kuthatha indawo yeefragati zakudala zeklasi yaseBremen.
Siyazi ukuba ziza kuquka umpu onamandla, uthotho lweemisiyeli ezichasene nomoya nezomkhumbi, kwakunye nezinye izinto ezinokungabonakaliyo, ezinjengemibono ye-radar, i-infrared kunye ne-acoustic encinane.
Ezinye izinto ezibalulekileyo ziquka ixesha elide lokugcina ukuze bakwazi ukuhambisa iminyaka emibini kude nezibuko.
Noko ke, ukulibaziseka okuqhubekayo kuye kwabangela ukuba iinqanawa ezintsha (ezakuvumela iJamani ukuba ibonise amandla ayo phesheya) zibe sele ziphelelwe lixesha xa ziqala ukusebenza, utsho uDie Zeit.
I-F125 enesiphene yafumana izihloko kunyaka ophelileyo, xa i-Navy yaseJamani yalela ngokusemthethweni ukufaka inqanawa kwaye yabuyisela kwi-Blohm & Voss Shipyard eHamburg.
Eli lixesha lokuqala ukuba iMarine ibuyisele inqanawa kwisikhululo senqanawa emva kokuba ifike.
Kwakungaziwa kangako ngezizathu zokubuyiselwa, kodwa amajelo eendaba aseJamani ayecaphula "iimpazamo ezinkulu zesoftware kunye neenkqubo" ezenza ukuba inqanawa ingasebenzi kakuhle xa ithunyelwa kumsebenzi wokulwa.
Iimpazamo zesoftware zazibaluleke ngokukodwa, kuba iinqanawa zodidi lweBaden-Wuerttemberg ziya kusetyenziswa ngabanini-zinqanawa abangama-120 - isiqingatha sabasebenzi ababekwizikhephe zakudala zodidi lweBremen.
Kwakhona, kwafunyaniswa ukuba inqanawa inobunzima obukhulu, nto leyo enciphisa ukusebenza kwayo kwaye iyakuthintela amandla oMkhosi wezasolwandle okongeza uhlaziyo lwexesha elizayo.
Kukholelwa ukuba i-7000 tonne "Rheinland-Pfalz" inzima ngokuphindwe kabini kunabanye iinqanawa ezikwiqela elifanayo ezasetyenziswa ngamaJamani kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Ukongezelela kwizixhobo ezinesiphene, ixabiso leprojekthi yonke, kuquka noqeqesho lwabasebenzi, liye labangela ingxaki.
Kucingelwa ukuba iye yafikelela kwi-3100 yezigidi zeedola (i-3600 yezigidi zeedola), endaweni ye-2200 yezigidi zeedola zokuqala.
Iingxaki ezibhekiswa kwiinqwelo-moya ezintsha zibaluleke kakhulu ngenxa yezikhumbuzo zakutshanje malunga nokuncitshiswa kwamandla olwandle eJamani.
Ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, uHans-Peter Bartels, intloko yekomiti yokhuselo yepalamente yaseJamani, wavuma ukuba iArmy "ihlala ingenazo iinqanawa ezinokuthumela".
Igosa lithi ingxaki iye yaba mandundu njengoko ixesha lihamba, kuba iinqanawa ezindala ziye zaphelelwa lixesha, kodwa azitshintshanga.
Uthe akakho omnye umkhosi weenqanawa ezinje ngeBaden-Wuerttemberg owawuza kujoyina iMarine.
I-National Trust Ihlolisisa Ubomi Obungafihliyo BamaBat
Olu phando lutsha lwenziwa kummandla waseScotland, uzama ukufumanisa indlela iimbethe ezisebenzisa ngayo umhlaba xa zikhangela ukutya.
Kulindeleke ukuba yonke into efunyenweyo ikhanyise ngakumbi kwindlela ezihamba ngayo izilwanyana ezihamba ngenqwelo-moya ibe iya kunceda ekujoliswe kuyo imisebenzi yokulondoloza.
Olu phando, olwenziwe yiNational Trust yaseScotland, luya kulandela iimbotyi eziqhelekileyo nezithetha nge-sopran, kunye neembotyi eziseDaubenton nezindlebe ezinde eziseInverewe Gardens eWester Ross.
Kuya kufakwa izixhobo zokurekhoda ezikhethekileyo kwiindawo eziphambili zepropathi ukuze zikwazi ukulandelela imisebenzi yeebhabhathane ngexesha lonyaka.
Abasebenzi kunye namavolontiya e-NHS baya kwenza uphando lweselula kunye neetekisi eziphathwayo.
Iingcali ziya kuhlolisisa izandi eziqokelelwa kwiirekhodi ukuze zifumanise ukuba zibiza kangakanani iimbethe, yaye zeziphi iintlobo.
Emva koko kuya kwenziwa ingxelo kunye nemephu yendawo yokuhlala ukuze kuveliswe umfanekiso opheleleyo wendalo kunye nokuziphatha kwayo.
URob Dewar, umcebisi wokulondolozwa kwendalo kwi-NTS, unethemba lokuba iziphumo ziya kutyhila ukuba zeziphi iindawo zendawo yokuhlala ezibaluleke kakhulu kwiibhabhathane nendlela uhlobo ngalunye olusebenzisa ngayo.
Le ngcaciso iza kuchaza izibonelelo zomsebenzi wokulawula indawo yokuhlala, njengokudala amadlelo nendlela amahlathi amele agcinwe ngayo ukuze kuhlale iimbovane nezinye iintlobo ezihambelanayo.
Iibhabhathane zaseScotland naseUnited Kingdom ziye zancipha kakhulu kule nkulungwane idluleyo.
Zisengozini ngenxa yokwakhiwa nokuphuhliswa kweendawo zazo zokuhlala nokulahleka kweendawo zazo zokuhlala.
Iifestile zomoya kunye neentambo zombane zinokuba yingozi kubo, njengama-insecticide kunye nezinye izinto zokwakha okanye ukuhlaselwa ziikati zasekhaya.
Iibhokhwe aziboni ngokwenene,
Kunoko, ngenxa yemikhwa yawo yokuzingela ebusuku, iindlebe zayo zinceda ngaphezu kwamehlo ayo ekufezekiseni injongo yayo.
Basebenzisa ubuchule obuphambili bokujonga indawo ezikuyo ukuze babone iinkumbi nezithuba ezikhokelela kwindiza yabo.
I-NTS, elawula ukhathalelo lwezakhiwo ezingaphezu kwe-270 zembali, iigadi ezingama-38 eziphambili kunye neehektare ezingama-76 000 zomhlaba kwilizwe liphela, ithatha umba weebhabhathane ngokungxamisekileyo.
Iinkokeli zelizwe lonke zenza uphando, zihlola izidleke, yaye maxa wambi ziyasindisa.
Le ntlangano iye yasungula indawo yokuqala neyokugcina kuphela yeebhabhathane eScotland kwiphondo laseThreave eDumfries naseGalloway, apho kuhlala khona iintlobo ezisibhozo kwezilishumi zeebhabhathane zaseScotland.
Umphathi wepropathi, uDavid Thompson, uthi le yindawo efanelekileyo kubo.
Wathi: "Ethreave, sinendawo entle yokudlala iimbethe".
"Sinezakhiwo ezindala, imithi emininzi yamaxesha amadala, kunye nendawo yokuhlala efanelekileyo.
Kodwa zininzi izinto ezingaziwa ngeebhabhathane, ngoko umsebenzi esiwenzayo apha nakwezinye iindawo uya kusinceda siqonde kakuhle oko zifuna ukukwenza ukuze ziphuhlise".
Uphinda athi kubalulekile ukujonga ukuba kukho na iimbotyi ngaphambi kokuba wenze imisebenzi yokugcina ngaphakathi kweendawo, kuba unokutshatyalaliswa ngokungazi ikoloni yokuzala kwaye ungabulala amabhinqa kunye neentlanzi ezingama-400, oko kuthetha ukuba uya kutshabalalisa bonke abantu bendawo.
Iibhokhwe zikhuselwe yaye akukho mthethweni ukubulala, ukuzikhathaza okanye ukuzikhathaza, okanye ukuchitha izindlu zazo.
UElizabeth Ferrell, igosa laseScotland elilawula iBat Conservation Trust, uye wakhuthaza uluntu ukuba luncedisane.
Wathi: "Kusasele izinto ezininzi esinokuzifunda ngeebhabhathane nezinye iintlobo ezininzi esingazaziyo ukuba zenzeka njani".
URonaldo uyazikhanyela izityholo zokudlwengula ngoxa amagqwetha akhe esukela iphephancwadi laseJamani
UChristiano Ronaldo ubhale iingxelo zokudlwengulwa njenge "fake news", esithi abantu "bafuna ukudalulwa" ngenxa yegama labo.
Amagqwetha akhe aye ayalelwa ukuba abhale ingxelo kwiphephandaba laseJamani iDer Spiegel, apho la mazwi ayepapashwa khona.
Umdlali wePortugal kunye neJuventus utyholwa ngokudlwengula ibhinqa laseMerika, uKathryn Mayorga, kwihotele yaseLas Vegas ngo-2009.
Uthi umtyhola ngokuba umhlawule i-375,000 yeedola ukuze afihle le ngxaki, njengoko ingxelo yeDer Spiegel ngoLwesihlanu.
Kwividiyo ye-Instagram Live esele ifumene abalandeli abazizigidi ezili-142 emva kweeyure ezimbalwa iindaba zipapashiwe, uRonaldo oneminyaka engama-33 ubudala, wabiza ingxelo ngokuthi "iindaba ezingezizo".
"Hayi, hayi, hayi, hayi, hayi.
Oko bakuthethileyo namhlanje akuchananga", utsho lo mntu uphumelele iGolide Ball izihlandlo ezihlanu, ejonge kwikhamera.
"Bafuna nje intengiso egameni lam.
Libali elifanayo eliqhelekileyo.
Bafuna ukuba ngamabhinqa ngokundithetha nje, kodwa kunjalo, andinakukwazi ukuyinqanda.
Ndingumntu onoyolo kwaye yonke into ilungile", wongeza lo mdlali, emomotheka.
Amagqwetha kaRonaldo alungiselela ukumangalelwa kweDer Spiegel ngenxa yezityholo ezibonakala kwinto abayibize ngokuba "ngumbhalo ongamkelekanga wokusolakala kobumfihlo", utshilo uReuters.
Igqwetha uChristian Schertz lithi lo mdlali uza kuzama ukufumana imbuyekezo "yokwenzakala kokuziphatha ngemali ehambelana nobunzima bokuphulukana, mhlawumbi yenye yezona zinto zimbi zenzekayo ekonakalisweni kwamalungelo akhe kwiminyaka yakutshanje".
Kubonakala ngathi le ngxaki yenzeka ngoJuni 2009 kwi-Palm Hotel and Casino eLas Vegas.
Emva kokudibana kwiklabhu yasebusuku, kuthiwa uRonaldo noMaurga baya egumbini lomdlali apho kuthiwa wadlwengula khona ngonyaka, ngokutsho kwamaxwebhu abhaliswe kwiNkundla yeSithili saseClark County eNevada.
UMorga uthi uRonaldo waguqa emva kweso siganeko waza wamxelela ukuba "ngama-99 ekhulwini" "ungumfana olungileyo" kwaye wayemtyumze loo "phesenti" iseleyo.
Le mibhalo ithi uRonaldo waqinisekisa ukuba aba babini babeneentlobano zesini, kodwa wavuma.
UMorga uthi waya emapoliseni waza wathatha iifoto zamatsholo esibhedlele, kodwa kamva wavuma ukufikelela kwisigqibo esingaphandle komthetho kuba "wayesoyika ukubuyisela" kwaye wayesoyika "ukuthotywa esidlangalaleni".
Lo mfazi uneminyaka engama-34 ubudala uthi uzama ukulichitha elo lungiselelo, kuba usengxakini.
Xa kwabakho le ngxaki, uRonaldo wayesele eza kudibana neReal Madrid evela eManchester United kwaye kule hlobo watshintshela kwiJuve, inkampani enkulu yebhola yase-Itali nge-100 yezigidi ze-€.
IBrexit: UK iya kuzisola ngokulahlekelwa ngabenzi beemoto
UK "uya kuzisola ubomi bakhe bonke" ukuba uya kuphulukana nesikhundla sayo njengomntu olawula ihlabathi ekwenzeni iimoto emva kweBrexit, utshilo uNobhala wezoShishino uGreg Clark.
Wongezelela ukuba "kukukhathaza" ukuba iToyota UK ibonise iBBC ukuba, ukuba iBritani iyashiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, imveliso iya kumiswa okwethutyana kumzi-mveliso wayo waseBurnaston, kufuphi neDerby.
"Sidinga isivumelwano", watsho uMnu.
Umvelisi waseJapan wathi ukulibaziseka kweentlawulo zamasiko kwimeko yeBrexit ngaphandle kwesivumelwano kunokubangela ilahleko yemisebenzi.
I-Burnaston, esenza i-Auris ne-Avensis yeToyota, ivelise iimoto ezimalunga ne-150,000 kunyaka ophelileyo, apho i-90 ekhulwini yathunyelwa kwamanye amazwe.
"Ndicinga ukuba, ukuba iBritani iyashiya i-EU ekupheleni kukaMatshi, kuya kubakho ukuyeka kwemveliso efektri yethu", watsho uMarvin Cooke, umlawuli-jikelele weToyota eBurnaston.
Abanye abavelisi beemoto base-UK baye babonisa ukuba banexhala malunga nokuphuma kwe-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, ngakumbi ngokunxulumene norhwebo oluphakathi kwemida; phakathi kwabo kukho iHonda, iBMW kunye neJaguar Land Rover.
Ngokomzekelo, iBMW ithi iza kuvala umzi-mveliso wayo weMini eOxford emva kwenyanga iBrexit iphelile.
Eyona nto ixhalabisa kakhulu abavelisi beemoto zizinto ezinokubakho kwiinkqubo zokudibanisa xa kukho iBrexit engenazo izivumelwano.
Umgca wemveliso kaToyota usekelwe kwindlela yemveliso elungeleleneyo (just in time okanye ngexesha lokugqibela) apho iinxalenye zifika rhoqo emva kwemizuzu engama-37 zivela kubathengisi base-UK nase-EU ukuze zenziwe iimoto ezicetywayo.
Ukuba u-UK uyishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ngo-Matshi 29, kusenokwenzeka ukuba kubekho ukuphazamiseka kumda okuya kubangela ukulibaziseka nokungabikho kwezinto zokwakha.
I-Toyota ithi ayinakukwazi ukugcina izinto eziza kufana nosuku olunye lwezinto ezisetyenziswayo kwimizi-mveliso yayo yaseDerbyshire, ibe oko kuya kubangela ukuba imveliso imiswe.
UMnu Clark wathi isicwangciso sikaTheresa May seChequers, esimisela ubudlelwane bexesha elizayo ne-EU, "sichaneke ngokuchanekileyo ukuze sikuphephe ukuhlolwa kwamathuba emida".
"Sifuna isivumelwano. Sifuna ukuba nesivumelwano esihle kakhulu esingagcini nje ngokusivumela ukuba siphume kakuhle kule meko ngoku kodwa kufuneka sisebenzise ithuba", utshilo kwinkqubo ye-BBC Radio 4 namhlanje.
"Ubungqina obuvela kwiToyota, phakathi kwabanye abavelisi abaninzi, bubonisa ukuba kufuneka sikwazi ukuqhubeka noko, kude kube ngoku, kube siseti yeendlela zokubonelela eziphumeleleyo".
I-Toyota ayizange ikwazi ukuchaza ixesha lokuyeka imveliso, kodwa yaqaphela ukuba, kwixesha elide, iindleko ezongeziweyo ziya kunciphisa ukhuphiswano lwesityalo kwaye ekugqibeleni iindleko.
UPeter Tsouvallaris, osebe eBurnaston iminyaka engama-24 kwaye ongumphathi we-Unite union kule ndawo, uthi amalungu ayo aya esoloko ekhathazekile: "Ngokwamava am, xa ezi zikhundla zilahlekile, azisoze zibuyele".
Isithethi sikaRhulumente sathi: "Sisungule isicwangciso esicacileyo nesinyanisekileyo esichaza ubudlelwane bethu bexesha elizayo ne-EU".
Umhlangano kaTrump noRosenstein unokuphinda ubekwe emva, ngokutsho kweNdlu yoMhlophe
Intlanganiso kaDonald Trump enobungozi obukhulu kunye noGqwetha-Jikelele uRod Rosenstein "inokuhlehliswa enye iveki", njengoko ingxabano malunga nomviwa weNkundla ePhakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh iqhubeka, iWhite House yathi ngeCawa.
URosenstein uphethe umsebenzi womcebisi okhethekileyo uRobert Mueller, ophanda ngokungenelela kunyulo lwaseRashiya, unxibelelwano phakathi kokuncedwa kukaTrump neRashiya, kunye nokungabikho kokusesikweni kumongameli.
Ukungathembani malunga nokuba uTrump uya kugqiba ekubeni agxothe i-vice-fiscal general okanye hayi, ngaloo ndlela, angenelele kuMueller kuye kwabangela ukuba iWashington ibe nexhala kangangeenyanga.
Ekuqaleni kwale nyanga, iNew York Times yathi uRosenstein wafota iingxoxo zakhe noTrump ngemakrofoni awayeyigqoke ukuze azame ukubhalisa uMongameli nge-25th Amendment.
URosenstein wakhanyela ukuba yinyaniso.
Noko ke, ngoMvulo ophelileyo waya kwiNdlu yoMhlophe, phakathi kweendaba apho kuthiwa wayeza kunikezela.
Endaweni yoko, kwabhengezwa intlanganiso noTrump (owayesakuba kwiZizwe eziManyeneyo eNew York ngelo xesha) ngoLwesine.
UTrump wathi "ngokwangoku angathanda" ukuyeka uRosenstein kodwa intlanganiso kwafuneka ihlehliswe ukuze kuthiwe akuyi kubakho ingxabano kwiNtlanganiso yeKomiti yezoBulungisa yeSenate yase-US apho uKavanaugh kunye nomnye wabasetyhini abamangalela ngokumhlasela ngokwesondo, uDkt. Christine Blasey Ford, bathetha.
NgoLwesihlanu uTrump wacela i-FBI ukuba iphonononge iimbambano ezityholwa nguKavanaugh kangangeveki, nangona oku kwakuya kubangela ukuba ukuvota kweSenate kuphazamiseke.
USihlalo kaTrump uSarah Sanders, ubonakele kwiFox News ngeCawa.
Xa ebuzwa ngomhlangano kaRosenstein, wathi: "Akukho mhla usekwe, unokuba kule veki okanye unokubekwa emva komnye, kuthathelwa ingqalelo yonke into eyenzekayo kwiNkundla Ephakamileyo.
Siza kuyenza le nto ngokuhamba kwexesha, yaye ndiza kuyinika amajelo eendaba, njengoko ndisoloko ndisenza".
Abanye abeendaba baya kulahla loo mazwi: USanders akazange anikezele iintetho kumbutho weendaba kwiNdlu yoMhlophe ukususela ngoSeptemba 10.
Umbonisi uChris Wallace wabuza ukuba ziziphi izizathu.
USanders wathi ukungabikho kwee-press wheels akubangelwa kukungafuni kwabanxibelelanisi beTV abaziphatha kakubi, nangona wathi: "Andiyi kuvumelana nokuqhayisa kwabo".
Emva koko, wathi unxibelelwano oluthe ngqo phakathi kukaTrump kunye neendaba luya kwanda.
"Uongameli wenza imibuzo neempendulo ezininzi kunaye nawuphi na omnye umongameli ngaphambi kwakhe", watsho, ngelixa wayecaphula ngaphandle kobungqina: "Sithe sachasana nezo nani".
USanders wathi iintlanganiso zamajelo eendaba ziya kuqhubeka, kodwa "ukuba amajelo eendaba anokukhetha ukubuza ngqo kumongameli waseMerika, ndicinga ukuba kungcono kakhulu ukuba azenze kum.
Sizamile ukwenza oku izihlandlo ezininzi yaye nisibonile sisenza oku izihlandlo ezininzi kwezi veki zidlulileyo, ngoko oku kuya kuthatha indawo yenkomfa yeendaba xa ninokuthetha nomongameli waseMerika".
UTrump udla ngokuphendula imibuzo xa eshiya iWhite House okanye xa ethatha inxaxheba kwiiseshoni zikawonke-wonke okanye kwiingqungquthela zonxibelelwano nabanye abantu abavela kwizikhundla eziphezulu.
Iinkomfa zonxibelelwano kunye naye zenzeka kuphela kumaxesha ambalwa.
Enyanisweni, kule veki, eNew York, umongameli wabonisa isizathu sokuba enjalo, apho wenza khona ukubonakala okungaqhelekanga, maxa wambi okungaqhelekanga, kwiintatheli ezazikho apho.
UMphathiswa WezeMpilo ubhalela abasebenzi base-EU kwi-NHS Scotland malunga noloyiko lwabo ngeBrexit
UMphathiswa WezeMpilo ubhalele abasebenzi base-EU abasebenza kwi-HHS yaseScotland ukuvakalisa umbulelo wabo kunye nomnqweno wabo wokuqhubeka nabo emva kweBrexit.
UJeane Freeman MSP wathumela ileta kwiinyanga nje ezintandathu ngaphambi kokuba i-UK ishiye i-EU.
Urhulumente waseScotland sele eza kuhlawula iindleko zokufaka izicelo zobumi kumalungu e-EU asebenza kwinkonzo karhulumente engaxhomekekanga kumandla aphakathi.
Kwileta yakhe, uFrieman wabhala: "Kule ntwasahlobo, kuye kwaqhubeka iingxoxo phakathi kwe-UK ne-EU zokuphuma apho kwakhethwa ukuba kuthathwe izigqibo ezijoliswe kuzo kule ntwasahlobo.
Nangona kunjalo, urhulumente wase-UK uye wanciphisa amalungiselelo okuhlangabezana nesimo esingenakuvunyelwana ngaso.
Ndiyazi ukuba oku kumele kube nzima kakhulu kuni.
Ngoko ke, ndifuna ukuqinisekisa ukuba ndiyayixabisa igalelo elenziwa ngamalungu onke abasebenzi, kungakhathaliseki ukuba ngabaluphi uhlanga.
Iingcali ezivela kulo lonke elase-EU nakwamanye amazwe zingenisa amava axabisekileyo nezakhono ezininzi eziqinisa nokuphucula umsebenzi wenkonzo yezempilo, ezixhamla izigulana kunye noluntu esilukhonzayo.
Ngokuqinisekileyo iScotland likhaya lenu yaye singathanda ukuqhubeka sinithemba".
UChristion Abercrombie uhlinzwa ngokukhawuleza emva kokwenzakala entloko
UChristion Abercrombie, umdlali weTennessee State Tigers, wangenelelwa ngokungxamisekileyo emva kokulimala entloko ngoMgqibelo ophelileyo, xa belahlekelwa yiVanderbilt Commodores ngo-31-27, uxele uMike Organ waseTennessee.
Umqeqeshi weTennessee State, uRod Reed, uxelele iintatheli ukuba ukwenzakala kwenzeka ngaphambi nje kokuba kuphumle.
