Ukwanda kwerhafu yokudluliselwa kwempahla iya kuhlawuliswa kubantu nakwimibutho engakhokheli rhafu e-UK kwaye loo mali iya kusetyenziselwa ukukhuthaza umgaqo-nkqubo karhulumente wokulwa nomceli-mngeni wasesitratweni.
Le ntlawulo, eyongezelelweyo kwirhafu yokuthumela, kuquka nokunyuka kwamanqanaba angeniswe kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo kwizindlu ezisetyenziswayo kunye nenkqubo yokuthenga-ku-let, inokuba ngama-3%.
