Apha ungabona iinkcukacha ezibalulekileyo ngePalu neDonggala, kwisiqithi saseSulawesi:
IPalu likomkhulu lephondo laseCentral Sulawesi, elikupheleni kwebhishi elincinci kunxweme olusentshona yesiqithi saseSulawesi, elinabemi abaqikelelwa kwi-379,800 ngo-2017.
Esi sixeko sasibhiyozela iminyaka engama-40 xa kwabakho inyikima ne-tsunami.
I-Donggala yindawo enegunya elisezantsi elisezantsi-ntshona kwisiqithi saseSulawesi.
I-regencia, eyindawo yolawulo ephantsi kwephondo, yayinabemi abaqikelelweyo abangama-299,200 ngo-2017.
Ukuloba nolimo ziintsika zoqoqosho kwiphondo laseCentral Sulawesi, ingakumbi kwingingqi enxweme yaseDonggala.
Iimigodi ze-nickel nazo zibalulekile kweli phondo, kodwa ikakhulu zixhomekeke eMorowali, kunxweme olwahlukileyo lwaseSulawesi.
IPalu neDonggala ziye zachaphazeleka ngama-tsunami izihlandlo eziliqela kule minyaka ingama-100 idluleyo, ngokutsho kwe-Indonesia Disaster Mitigation Agency.
Ngowe-1938, i-tsunami yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwe-200 yaza yatshatyalalisa izindlu ezininzi eDonggala.
I-tsunami yahlasela kwintshona yeDonggala ngo-1996, yabulala abantu abasithoba.
I-Indonesia ikwiBhanti Lomlilo yasePasifiki, indawo enenyikima enkulu, yaye idla ngokuduma rhoqo.
Apha ngezantsi sichaza ezinye zeenyikima ezinkulu neetsunami zeminyaka yakutshanje:
Ngowama-2004: Inyikima enkulu kunxweme olusentshona yephondo laseAceh eIndonesia, kumantla eSumatra, ibangele i-tsunami ngoDisemba 26 eyachaphazela amazwe ali-14 yaza yabulala abantu abangama-226.000 kunxweme loLwandlekazi lwaseIndiya.
Ngo-2005: Uthotho lweenyikima ezinkulu zenzeka kunxweme olusentshona yeSumatra ekupheleni kukaMatshi nasekuqaleni kuka-Aprili.
Kwakukho amawaka abantu ababuleweyo kwisiqithi saseNias, kufuphi nonxweme lwaseSumatra.
Ngowama-2006: Inyikima enamandla angama-6.8 yahlasela ummandla osemazantsi eJava, esona siqithi sinabantu abaninzi eIndonesia, yaza yabangela i-tsunami eyachaphazela unxweme olusemazantsi, yabulala abantu abamalunga nama-700.
Ngo-2009: Inyikima enkulu, enamandla ayi-7,6 yazamazama kufuphi nesixeko sasePadang, ikomkhulu lephondo laseNtshona Sumatra.
Kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 100.
Ngo-2010: Inyikima enamandla ayi-7.5 yahlasela esinye seziqithi zaseMentawai kufuphi neSumatra, yaza yabangela itsunami eyayimalunga neemitha ezili-10 ubude, yabhidliza amashumi amawaka eedolophu yaza yabulala abantu abamalunga nama-300.
Ngo-2016: Inyikima enzulu encinane yabetha i-Pidi Jaya Regency e-Aceh, ibangela umonakalo kunye nexhala njengoko ikhumbula ukubhujiswa kwenyikima ne-tsunami ka-2004.
Ngeli xesha zange kubekho tsunami, kodwa ukuwa kwezakhiwo kwabulala abantu abangaphezu kwe-100.
Ngo-2018: Isiqithi esikhenkethi saseLombok (eIndonesia) safumana uthotho lweenyikima ezinkulu ezenza abantu abangaphezu kwama-500 bafa, uninzi lwabo lusemazantsi esiqithi.
Le nyikima yabhidliza amawaka ezakhiwo yaye amawaka abakhenkethi aba ngamakhoboka.
Unyana omdala kaSarah Palin ubanjwe etyholwa ngokurhwaphiliza amakhaya
UTrac Palin, unyana omdala owayengumongameli waseAlaska nomviwa weSekela likaMongameli uSarah Palin, ubanjwe ngezityholo zokugweba.
UPalin, oneminyaka engama-29 ubudala, ohlala eWasillah, eAlaska, wabanjwa ngokusolwa ngokuba ebandakanyeka kugonyamelo lwasekhaya, ephazamisa ingxelo yolwaphulo-mthetho lwasekhaya, kwaye enxamnye nokubanjwa, ngokutsho kwengxelo epapashwe ngoMgqibelo ngamapolisa aseAlaska.
Ngokutsho kwengxelo yamapolisa, xa omnye umntu awayeqhelene naye wazama ukubiza amapolisa ukuze abhengeze ulwaphulo-mthetho, wayithabatha ifowuni yakhe.
UPalin ugwetyelwe ukuvalelwa entolongweni eMat-Su Pretrial Facility kwaye ugcinwe kwibhanti engaqinisekanga yeedola ezingama-500, kubika i-KTUU.
Wavela enkundleni ngoMgqibelo, apho wavakalisa ngokuqinisekileyo engenatyala xa wayecelwa ukuba enze ingxelo, kuxelwe yinkqubo.
UPalin unetyala lamatyala amathathu angaphantsi kweBakala A, nto leyo ethetha ukuba unokuba sentolongweni unyaka omnye aze afumane imali eyi-250.000.
Kwakhona utyholwa ngesityholo esincinane, esihlawulwa usuku entolongweni kunye ne-2 000 yeedola.
Esi asisihlandlo sokuqala uPalin etyholwa.
NgoDisemba 2017, watyholwa ngokuhlasela uyise, uTodd Palin.
Unina, uSarah Palin, wabiza amapolisa ukuze abike ngokuhlaselwa.
Eli tyala likwiNkundla yamaNcedisi aseAlaska.
NgoJanuwari 2016, watyholwa ngokuhlaselwa ekhaya, ngokuphazamisa ukubhengezwa kwezenzo zobundlobongela basekhaya kunye nokuba nesibhamu xa enxilile, ngokunxulumene nesiganeko.
Umtshakazi wakhe wathi wamtyakatya ebusweni.
Amaqela amaninzi amajoni asele ekhonza e-Iraq agxeka uSarah Palin ngo-2016 ngokudibanisa ukuziphatha kwakhe ngogonyamelo nokuxinezeleka emva kokuhlaselwa yintlungu ngenxa yokuba wayekhonza e-Iraq.
