Umtshutshisi welizwe lonke ufuna isigwebo sokufa kumntu osolwayo ngokuhlaselwa kweentoriki eNew York
Umtshutshisi waseNew York ufuna ukufa kukaSayfullo Saipov, osolwayo kwintlaselo yamagorha kwisixeko saseNew York eyabulala abantu abasibhozo, isohlwayo esingaqhelekanga esingazange senziwe kweli lizwe ngenxa yetyala laseburhulumenteni ukususela ngo-1953.
USaipov oneminyaka engama-30 ubudala kuthiwa wasebenzisa iveni ekrentiweyo yeHome Depot ukuhlasela umzila webhayisekile kwiWest Side Highway eMzantsi Manhattan ngo-Oktobha odlulileyo, elahla abakhweli kunye nabakhweli bebhayisekile ababekumendo wakhe.
Ukuze kuqinisekiswe isigwebo sokufa, ababhekisi bamangalelwa kufuneka babonise ukuba uSaipov wabulala ngabom amaxhoba asibhozo waza wabangela ngabom ukwenzakala emzimbeni, ngokutsho kwesibhengezo senjongo yesigwebo sokufa, esifakwe kwiSithili saseMzantsi New York.
Zombini ezi zityholo zinokuxoxwa ngesigwebo sokufa, ngokutsho kwexwebhu leNkundla.
Kwiiveki ezimbalwa emva kokuhlaselwa, i-jury enkulu yase-Federal yafaka isityholo kwii-Saipov kwiibango ezingama-22 ezibandakanya amatyala asibhozo obugwenxa obuxhaswe ngumthetho olungelelanisiweyo, oqhele ukusetyenziswa ngabasemagunyeni base-Federal kula matyala, kunye netyala lobundlobongela nokutshatyalaliswa kweemoto.
Abaqeshi bathi lo mlo wawufuna ulungelelwaniso oluhle, yaye uSaipov wayenza ngendlela engekho sikweni, enobundlobongela neyonakeleyo.
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wabangela ukwenzakala, ukonakala kunye nelahleko kwiintsapho kunye nabahlobo bakaDiego Enrique Angelini, uNicolas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza noAlexander Damian Pagnucco, kuchazwe kwisaziso seenjongo.
Abahlanu kwabo babulawa ngabantu baseArgentina.
Sele kudlule iminyaka elishumi ukususela kwixesha elidlulileyo apho iSithili saseMzantsi New York sasiye saqulunqa ityala lokufa.
Umtyholwa, uKhalid Barnes, wafunyanwa enetyala lokubulala abantu ababini ababethengisa iziyobisi, kodwa ekugqibeleni wagwetywa ubomi bakhe bonke ngoSeptemba 2009.
Ixesha lokugqibela apho isigwebo sokufa sasibulawa kwicala likaRhulumente waseNew York nguJulius noEthel Rosenberg ngo-1953. Lo mtshato wabulawa emva kokuba bagwetywe ngokuqhatha ukuhlola i-Soviet Union ngexesha leMfazwe ebandayo kwiminyaka emibini ngaphambili.
Bobabini uRosenberg babulawa kwisitulo sombane ngoJuni 19, 1953.
USaipov, ongumphambukeli ovela eUzbekistan, wabonisa ukungazisola kwakhe kwiintsuku neenyanga emva kokuhlaselwa, ngokutsho kwamaxwebhu enkundla.
Amapolisa athi wathi uphando lwenza ukuba azive ekhululekile.
Ngokutsho kwesityholo, uSaipov uxelele abasemagunyeni ukuba ukuhlaselwa kwakhe waphefumlelwa kukubukela iividiyo ze-ISIS kwifowuni yakhe.
Kwakhona wacela ukuba ibhanti ye-ISIS iphakanyiswe kwigumbi lakhe lasebhedlele, kutsho amapolisa.
Uye wavuma ukungabikho kwetyala kumatyala ayi-22.
UDavid Patton, omnye wabameli abajongene nobulungiseleli bukaRhulumente abamele uSaipov, uthe 'bayacaphuka' ngesigqibo somtshutshisi.
Sikholelwa ukuba isigqibo sokufuna isigwebo sokufa kunokuba samkele isibhengezo sokuba netyala kunye nesigwebo sentolongo esingenabomi bokukhululwa, siya kuqhubeka sisenza intlungu yezi ziganeko kubo bonke abantu ababandakanyekayo, utshilo uPatton.
Iqela lokukhusela uSaipov lacela amagqwetha ukuba angafuni isigwebo sokufa.
