Imfazwe yorhwebo phakathi kwe-United States ne-China inokuyinceda iBeijing
Iingxelo zokuqala zokulwa imfazwe yorhwebo phakathi kweUnited States neTshayina zazingekho, yaye nangona kusekho ixesha elide ngaphambi kokuba imfazwe iphele, iingcali zithi ukuhlukana phakathi kwamazwe kunokuyinceda iBeijing.
UDonald Trump, umongameli waseMerika, wakhupha isilumkiso sokuqala ekuqaleni konyaka ngokufaka iirhafu kwizithuthi eziphambili zaseTshayina, ezinje ngeepaneli zelanga, intsimbi kunye nealuminiyam.
Eyona nto ibalulekileyo yenzeka kule veki, kuba kukho iirhafu ezintsha ezichaphazela iidola ezingama-200,000 ezigidi (i-150,000 ezigidi zeengqekembe zeengqekembe) zeemveliso, ezihlawulisa isiqingatha semveliso engenayo e-United States evela e-China.
Kuzo zonke izihlandlo, iBeijing iye yaziphindezela ngokufanayo, kutshanje isebenzise iirhafu eziphakathi kweepesenti ezintlanu ukuya kwezilishumi kwiimveliso zaseMerika ezixabisa iidola ezili-60 zamawaka ezigidi.
I-China iye yazibophelela ekufaniseni ukuhlaselwa yi-US, yaye akubonakali ngathi uqoqosho lwesibini ngobukhulu emhlabeni luya kuhla ngokukhawuleza.
Ukufumana iWashington ukuba ibuye emva kwakuya kuthetha ukunikezela kwiimfuno, kodwa ukuzithoba esidlangalaleni e-United States kwakuya kuba lihlazo kakhulu kuMongameli waseTshayina uXi Jinping.
Nangona kunjalo, iingcali zithi ukuba iBeijing idlala kakuhle, uxinzelelo lweMfazwe yoRhwebo yaseMerika lunokunceda iChina ixesha elide ngokunciphisa ukuxhomekeka phakathi kwezoqoqosho.
Ukuthi isigqibo esikhawulezayo sezepolitiki eWashington okanye eBeijing sinokubangela ukuba kubekho iimeko zokuqalisa ukuwa kwezoqoqosho kulo naliphi na ilizwe liyingxaki enzulu kunokuba ababukeli beye bavuma ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, utshilo uAbigail Grace, ongumphandi-mngundoqo weCentre for New American Security, owenza uphando ngeAsia kwiCabinet Strategic.
ISyria ilungele ukuba abaphambukeli babuyele, utshilo uMphathiswa Wezangaphandle
ISiriya ithi ilungele ukubuyela kwabasemzini ngokuzithandela ize icele uncedo ekwakheni ilizwe eliye labhidlizwe yimfazwe elidlule iminyaka esixhenxe.
Kwintetho yakhe ngaphambi kweNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo, uMphathiswa Wezangaphandle uWalid al-Moualem wathi iimeko zelizwe ziya ziphucuka.
Imeko yasemagqabini namhlanje izinzile kwaye ikhuselekile ngenxa yenkqubela eyenziweyo ekulweni nobugrogrisi, utshilo.
Urhulumente uyaqhubeka nokuhlaziya iindawo ezonakaliswe ngabagqugqisi ukuze azame ukubuyisela imilo.
Zonke iimeko zilungiselelwe ukuba abaphambukeli abaphulukene nelizwe labo babuyele kulo ngokuzithandela ngenxa yobundlobongela kunye namanyathelo oqoqosho angavaniyo achaphazela ubomi babo bemihla ngemihla kunye neendlela zabo zokuziphilisa.
IZizwe Ezimanyeneyo ziqikelela ukuba ukususela oko imfazwe yaqalisa ngo-2011, abantu baseSiriya abangaphezu kwezigidi eziyi-5,5 baye babaleka kweli lizwe.
Kukho ezinye izigidi ezithandathu zabantu abasaphila kweli lizwe yaye badinga uncedo.
UAl-Moualem wavuma ukuba urhulumente waseSiriya uza kuba nombulelo ngoncedo ekwakheni ilizwe eliyinkxwaleko.
Kodwa wagxininisa ukuba akayi kwamkela uncedo olunemibandela okanye uncedo lwamazwe akhuthaze ukuvukela.
IYurophu yenziwa ngeRyder Cup eParis
Iqela laseYurophu liphumelele iRyder Cup ka-2018 ngokutshabalalisa iqela laseMntla Melika ngomlinganiselo wokugqibela we-16,5 ukuya ku-10,5 kwiLe Golf National, ngaphandle kweParis (eFransi).
I-United States ngoku inokuphumelela kwimihlaba yaseYurophu ngokulandelanayo ukususela kwixesha lokugqibela apho iphumelele khona iRyder Cup eYurophu ngo-1993.
IYurophu yafumana isithsaba xa iqela likaputeni waseDenmark uThomas Bjorn lafumana amanqaku ayi-14.5 aza kuhlasela iUnited States.
Inkwenkwezi yaseMntla yaseMerika uPhil Mickelson, ekwakumele alwe kuyo yonke le nkundla, yaphosa indawo yakhe yokuphuma emanzini kumngxuma 16 par 3, ngaloo ndlela ivuma ukoyiswa nguFrancesco Molinari.
Umdlali wegalufa waseItali uMolinari wabonakala kuzo zonke iirandi zakhe, waba ngomnye wabadlali abane abangazange bafumane i-5-0-0 ukususela oko kwaqala ifomathi yangoku yomdyarho ngo-1979.
Umdlali waseMerika uJordan Spieth wehla ngo-5 no-4 kumdlali owela kwizinga eliphantsi kwiqela laseYurophu, umDanish Thorbjorn Olesen.
Umdlali oyintloko wehlabathi, uDustin Johnson, wehla ngo-2-1 kwiNgesi uIan Poulter, owayengade adlale iRyder Cup yakhe yokugqibela.
USergio García waseSpain, umakadebona osele eneNdebe zeRyder ezisibhozo, waba ngowona mYurophu unqobe kakhulu kulo mdlalo, eneziphumo ezingama-25,5 kwimidlalo yakhe.
