Ukuhlaziywa kweDada elibomvu: Ukuncipha kweePinellas, Manatee neSarasota
Ingxelo entsha yeFlorida Fish and Wildlife Commission ibonisa ukuba inani leentlanzi ezibomvu liyancipha kwiindawo ezikufutshane neTampa Bay.
Ngokutsho kweFWC, iimeko zokudumba ngokungaqhelekanga ziyaxelwa kwiindawo ezikwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte naseCollier, nto leyo ebonisa ukuba izidumbu zinciphile.
Ukuqhakaza kwe-red tide kubandakanya malunga ne-130 miles yolwandle ukusuka ePinellas County ngasentla ukuya kwi-Lee County ngasentla.
Unokufumana iindawo ezingaqhelekanga malunga neekhilomitha ezili-10 kunxweme lweHillsborough County, kodwa kwiindawo ezimbalwa xa kuthelekiswa neveki ephelileyo.
Kwakhona kuye kwafunyanwa umlambo obomvu kwiphondo lasePasco.
Kule veki iphelileyo, kuye kwaxelwa malunga nokuxinana okuphakathi kwiPhondo lasePinellas nakunxweme lwayo, ukuxinana phakathi kokuphantsi kunye nokuphezulu kunxweme lweHillsborough County, ukuxinana okuphantsi ukuya phezulu kwiPhondo laseManatee, ukuxinana okuphantsi ukuya phezulu kwiPhondo laseSarasota nakunxweme lwayo, ukuxinana okuphakathi ukuya phezulu kwiPhondo laseCharlotte, ukuxinana okuphantsi ukuya phezulu kwiPhondo laseLee nakunxweme lwayo, kunye nokuxinana okuphantsi kwiPhondo laseCollier.
Kukho iingxelo zokuba kukho iingxaki zokuphefumla eziqhubekayo kwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee naseCollier.
Akukho ngxaki yokuphefumla eFlorida eseMantla Ntshona kwiveki ephelileyo.
